var book = {
	"name": "UYOBI",
	"numChapters": 42,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> KwelaseUze kwakukho indoda egama linguYobi. Wayengumfo olungileyo engenabala, umfo omhlonelayo uThixo eyithiyile into embi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Wayenoonyana abasixhenxe neentombi ezintathu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Wayefuyile eneegusha ezingamawaka asixhenxe, amawaka amathathu eenkamela, newaka leenkabi zeenkomo, needonki ezingamakhulu amahlanu. Ngokunjalo ke lo mfo wayenenyambalala yezicaka. Ke uYobi lo wayeyeyona ndoda isisinhanha kubo bonke abantu kwelasempuma.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ke kaloku oonyana bakaYobi babedla ngokuqokelelana benze umbhiyozo endlwini yalowo yayiyimini yakhe. Babemema noodade babo abathathu ukuza kutya basele kunye nabo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Wakuba lo mbhiyozo ujikeleze kubo bonke uYobi wayedla ngokubabiza abantwana bakhe ukuze abahlambulule. Wayevuka kusasa kakhulu, abenzele amadini atshiswayo ngabanye ngabanye. Kaloku uYobi wayesithi: “Mhlawumbi kusenokwenzeka ukuba abantwana bam bonile bamtshabhisa uThixo ezintliziyweni zabo.” Wayesenjenjalo ke uYobi ngayo yonke imihla yakhe.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngamhla uthile izidwangube zakwaThixo zaya *kuNdikhoyo, noSathana ke ephakathi kwazo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> UNdikhoyo ke wathi kuSathana: “Uvela phi wena?” Ke yena uSathana waphendula uNdikhoyo wathi: “Ndivela ekubhaduleni, ndisihla ndinyuka, ndijikeleza ehlabathini.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> UNdikhoyo wathi kuSathana: “Usiqondile kodwa isicaka sam uYobi? Akakho onjengaye ehlabathini liphela. Yena ngumfo othembekileyo ongenabala, indoda emhlonelayo uThixo, eyicezelayo into embi.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> USathana wamphendula uNdikhoyo wathi: “Kungaba kungelize na ukuba uYobi afumane amoyike uThixo?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kaloku wena umbiyele; usoloko umphahlile yena nendlu yakhe, nako konke anako. Uwuthamsanqele wonke umsebenzi wezandla zakhe, yaye nemfuyo yakhe iye isanda ngokwanda elizweni.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nangoku ke khawolule isandla sakho uchukumise yonke le nto anayo; uya kubona, uya kukushwabulela nawe lo!”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> UNdikhoyo ke wathi kuSathana: “Kulungile ke, ungayenza into oyenzayo kwinto yonke anayo, kodwa uze ungakhe ulinge umchukumise yena siqu.” USathana ke wemka apho phambi koNdikhoyo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngenye imini xa oonyana bakaYobi neentombi zakhe babebhiyoza besitya besela endlwini yenkulu yakhe,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> kwafika isigidimi kuYobi, sathi: “Besilima ngeenkabi, zona iidonki zisitya kwalapho kufutshane;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> kwaza kwagaleleka amaSabha, asihlasela, azithimba ezo nkomo needonki. Ke zona izicaka zakho azibulele ngekrele; kusinde mna ndedwa ukuze ndikwazise.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Eso sicaka sathi sisathetha njalo kwafika esinye isigidimi, sathi: “Zonke iigusha zakho ngokunjalo nabelusi zibethwe ngumbane zafa; kusinde mna ndedwa ukuze ndikwazise.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Sisathetha njalo kwagaleleka esinye, safika sathi: “Sihlaselwe ngamaqela amathathu amaKaledi, afika azithimba iinkamela, abelusi ababulala ngekrele, yandim ndedwa osindayo ukuze ndikwazise.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Eso sigidimi sathi sisachaza njalo, kwagaleleka esinye, safika sathi: “Oonyana neentombi zakho bebesendlwini yonyana wakho omkhulu, bebhiyoza, besitya, besela iwayini,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> kwaza kwasuka kwavuthuza inkanyamba, ivela ngasentlango. Isuke yadlikidla amacala omane endlu leyo, yabawela abantwana abo, bafela apho bonke; ndim ndedwa osindileyo. Ewe, ndim kuphela osindileyo ukuze ndikubikele.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kwesi sithuba ke uYobi waphakama, wakrazula umnweba wakhe, wayigugula intloko yakhe, waza ke wee guqaqa wanqula,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> wathi: “Ndazalwa nguma ndizé, ndaye ke ndiya kunduluka ndikwazé. NguNdikhoyo onikayo, ikwanguye nothathayo. Malidunyiswe igama likaNdikhoyo!”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kuyo yonke le ntlekele uYobi zange one okanye akhalazele uThixo."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kwakhona kwathi kwakufika usuku lokuba izidwangube zakwaThixo zihlanganisane phambi *koNdikhoyo noSathana wabakho phakathi kwazo ukuze avele phambi koNdikhoyo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> UNdikhoyo wathi kuSathana: “Uvela phi wena?” Ke yena uSathana wamphendula uNdikhoyo wathi: “Ndivela ekubhaduleni, ndisihla ndinyuka, ndijikeleza ehlabathini.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> UNdikhoyo wathi kuSathana: “Usiqondile kodwa isicaka sam uYobi? Akakho onjengaye ehlabathini liphela. Yena ngumfo othembekileyo ongenabala, indoda emhlonelayo uThixo, eyicezelayo into embi. Nangoku usabambelele ekuthembekeni kwakhe, nangona wena undixhokonxele ekubeni ndimonakalisele ngaphandle kwesizathu.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> USathana ke wamphendula uNdikhoyo wathi: “Hayi kaloku, isikhumba ngesikhumba! Umntu angancama yonke into anayo ngenxa yobomi bakhe.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nangoku ungathi ukhe wolula isandla sakho wamchukumisa enyameni nasemathanjeni akhe, angakushwabulela nawe lo.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> UNdikhoyo ke wathi kuSathana: “Kulungile ke, nanko ndimnikela esandleni sakho; nto nje uze ungabuchukumisi ubomi bakhe.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> USathana ke wemka apho phambi koNdikhoyo, wafika wabetha uYobi ngamathumba oyikekayo athi tshitshilili ukuqalela elunyaweni ukuya kutsho entloko.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ke kaloku uYobi wahlala eluthuthwini, wathatha iceba lembiza, wazonwaya ngalo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Inkosikazi yakhe yathi kuye: “Nangoku usabambelele kule ntembeko yakho? Mqalekise lo Thixo, ufe kube kanye!”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ke yena wamphendula wathi: “Ukuthetha kwakho nqwa nokomfazi ongaqiqiyo! Kakade, uthi masiyolelwe zizinto ezintle zodwa esiziphiwa nguThixo, singazamkeli ezimbi?” Kuyo yonke le ntlekele uYobi zange one ngomlomo wakhe.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ke uYobi wayenezihlobo ezithathu ezathi zeva ngayo yonke le nkxwaleko emhleleyo. Yaseso isihlobo ke seza sivela kowaso umzi, inguElifazi waseTeman, uBhildadi waseShuwa, noZofare waseNama. Zazivumelene ngento yokuba ziye kumkhuza uYobi, zimthuthuzele.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ke kaloku zathi zisemgama zambona uYobi, phofu ke azamazi. Kambe ke zathi zakumqonda zangqukruleka zalila, zakrazula iminweba yazo, zizigalela ngothuli entloko, ziphosa uthuli emoyeni.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ke kaloku zahlala naye apho phantsi iintsuku ezisixhenxe nobusuku bazo kungekho nasinye sithetha naye, kuba zazibona ukuba umva-ndedwa wakhe mkhulu gqitha."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Emva koko ke uYobi wathetha wawuqalekisa umhla awazalwa ngawo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ewe, uYobi uvakele esithi:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Ngamana zange wathwasa umhla endazalwa ngawo; nditsho nobo busuku apho kwathiwa: ‘Namhlanje kukhawulwe indoda!’",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Akwaba loo mini yayingumnyam' ombonde-mbonde; mini leyo noThixo kweliphezulu angayihoyanga; mini ingazange yabonana nokukhanya!",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngeyambathiswe sisiphitha-nyongo sobumnyama; ngeyisityekelwe ziingqimba zamafu. Loo mini ngeyirhwaqeliswe sisithokothoko sobumnyama;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> nobo busuku ngebambathiswe sisithokothoko, suka àbabalelwa kwimihla yonyaka, àbakhankanywa phakathi kweentsuku zeenyanga.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ewe, akwaba obo busuku babuludlolo; akwaba kwakungavakalanga kumemelela kubo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Iinkintsela zokuqalekisa imihla ngeziyiqalekisile loo mini; ngeziyifunze ngengwenya.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Iinkwenkwezi zangorhatya ngezimnyama; loo mini ngeyilindele ukusa kodwa kungaze kufike, nomsobomvu ungaze uthi chapha!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kaloku ayizivalanga iingcango zesizalo esandizalayo, ayandiphephisa kule nkxwaleko ndikuyo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Kwakungani ndingafi ndingekazalwa nje, okanye ndife ndisazalwa?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngani ukuba uma andisingathe emadolweni? Khona, kwakutheni ukuba andincancise ibele?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kuba xa bekungenjalo, ngendalala ndazola; ewe, ngendiphumle kobandayo,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ndawonye nezikumkani namaphakathi, lawo awavusayo amanxuwa;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ngoku ngendikunye namatshawe, azindlu zazizele yigolide nesiliva.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngani ukuba ndingafihlwanga njengomphunzo, njengemveku engalibonanga ilanga?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kaloku apho nezikhohlakali azikhathazi mntu, nabadiniweyo baxhamla ukuphumla.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Khona amabanjwa azonwabele; ahlukene nokungxoliswa yinduna yawo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Apho bandawonye abaphakamileyo nabaphantsi, nkqu nekhoboka likhululekile kumninilo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Ngani ukuba abaza kubandezeleka balibone ilanga, abangcungcuthekayo babudle ubomi?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bona balangazelela ukufa, kungafiki noko; bakuzingela ngathi bafuna ubutyebi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Abavuyi bayachulumacha, bachwayitile xa bedibana nengcwaba.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ngani ukuba balibone ilanga abandlela imfiliba, abo babiyelweyo nguThixo?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kuba ukutya kwam yincwina; ukugcuma kumpompoza njengamanzi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kuba ndihlelwa zezo zinto zindinkwantyisayo; ezindinxunguphalisayo zezona zindihlelayo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Andinako ukuzola, ndingenako nokonwaba; Andifumani kuphumla, kuba ndasoloko ndijijitheka.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kwesi sithuba ke kuphendule uElifazi waseTeman, wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ngaba xa umntu enokukuphendula awungekhathazeki kodwa? Phofu ke ibingubani onokuthula nje?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Khumbula kaloku ukuba baninzi abantu obaqeqeshileyo, ubakhuthaza ubomeleza abazandla zinomkhinkqi!",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngamazwi akho ubaxhasile abakhubekayo, wabaqinisa abamadolo agevezelayo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namhlanje ke kungawe, naku ke wena ungenakunyamezela; ewe, zidla kuwe, ngoku ke wena suka wadideka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Andithi na kaloku wena ukholosa ngokuhlonela uThixo? Ewe kaloku, qamela ngobunyulu beendlela zakho, ukholose!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Hayi kaloku, khawuzikise ukucinga; ngubani owakha wabhanga emsulwa? Ingubani khona owakhe watshabalala kodwa engenabala?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ke kwawam amava, abalima ububi, batyale inkathazo, bavuna loo nto bayilimileyo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ewe kaloku, ngokuphefumla nje kukaThixo batsho badake; ngenene yena ufutha kube kanye batsho baphel' emehlweni!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bona banjengeengonyama ezikroboke amazinyo: nokuba ziyagquma zibhavumle ngokurhwaqelisayo,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ziyatshabalala kukuswela amaxhoba, nawo amathole azo asuke abe ziintsali.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Ndakha ndee rhithi udaba bunkente-nkente; ewe, iindlebe zam zeva amarhe ngathi kuyasetyezwa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kanye ngaloo mathuba emiva-ndedwa yemibono ebusuku, xa kanye ndikobentlombe,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> suka ndarhwaqela ndankwantya, ada amathambo am anengevane.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nako ke kusithi phinzi into phambi kwam; hayi ke, ndahlathuzela ngamanwele!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nantso ke, suka yema bhunxe! Hayi, andibanga nakuyinakana mpela. Phofu wona umthinzi wabe uphambi kwam – hayi ke, kwathi cwaka, ndada ndeva ilizwi lisithi:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ‘Ngab' ingenzeka na into yokuba umntu abe lilungisa kunoThixo? Umntu angaba nyulu ngaphezu koMdali wakhe?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Andithi na kaloku nezicaka zakwakhe akazithembi? Nditsho nezithunywa zakhe azimkholisi kwaphela.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Babengoobani ke abantu abahlala ezindlwini zodaka, abantu abasiseko siluthuli, abasuka batyumke njengenundu?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Umntu ungambona ekhona kusasa, kanti ke kuya kuthi kurhatyela abe selengasekho; ewe, utshabalala kuphele engakhange aqondakale!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kaloku nelo nqugwala lakhe lisuka lincothulwe, ke yena afe engekabufumani bona ubulumko!’"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Danduluka kaloku, ukhale, ubone ukuba ukhona oya kuphendula! He-e-e, uza kubhenela kwesiphi ke ngoku isithunywa?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ngenene izityhakala zizigwinta ngengcwangu yazo; lona ikhwele yimfeketho ephelela ekufeni.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ndakha ndasibona isityhakala sihluma; suka ke mna ndaliqalekisa elo khaya laso.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Oonyana baso basesichengeni; nasenkundleni basisisulu, akukho bani ubahlangulayo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Isivuno saso sityiwa zizilambi, zisicubungula naphakathi kwameva. Amabawa ayaburhogola ubutyebi baso.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kaloku inkxwaleko ayiphumi luthulini, ibe ke nenkathazo ayintshuli mhlabeni.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Umntu nenkathazo ngumtya nethunga, kwanjengokuba intlantsi ihamba nomlilo!”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Kambe ke, ukuba ibindim, bendiya kubhenela kuThixo, ndiyaneke phambi kwakhe imeko yam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kaloku nguye owenza izigigaba ezingenakugoca-gocwa; imimangaliso yakhe ayiphele ndawo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Nguye onisa imvula emhlabeni, amasimi awanyakamise ngamanzi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Yena ngumphakamisi wabadelekileyo; ke bona abasezinyembezini uyabathuthuzela.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kaloku yena uyaliphuthisa icebo lesindwebi, ize imizamo yaso ibuye nemband' esikhova.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Izilumko uzitsho zixakane nobuqhokolo bazo, ize imizabalazo yazo yobuqhophololo ibhange ngesaquphe.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kwakuba njalo ke kutsho kuhlw' emini kuzo; kuthi kusemin' emaqanda, zona zitotobe ziphampathe ngathi kukwabhadakazi!",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> NguThixo obakhuselayo abahlelelekileyo ekutyholweni; nguye obahlangula esandleni sabomeleleyo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngoko ke likhona ithemba nakumahlwempu; ke zona izikhohlakali zitsho zisikw' umlomo!",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Ewe, unenyhweba umntu olulekwa nguThixo; ngoko ke sukuyidela ingqeqesho kaSomandla!",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kaloku yena uyenzakalisa, abuye abophe; kanti kwayena uyabetha, abuye aphilise ngezandla zakhe.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Yena uyaphinda-phinda ukukuhlangula ezinkathazweni, kanti ke ekugqibeleni akuyi kuba sachukunyiswa bubi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ngexesha lendlala uya kukuhlangula ekufeni; ukanti emfazweni uya kukusindisa ekreleni.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngokunjalo uya kukukhusela kwintlebendwane, ungabi naxhala ngexesha lonxunguphalo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Unxunguphalo nendlala ziya kuba yimfeketho kuwe, ungawaxhaleli namarhwamncwa ehlabathi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Uya kunqophisana namatye asemathambekeni, kubekho uxolo phakathi kwakho namarhamncwa asendle.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Umzi wakho uya kuhlala ukhuselekile, nasesibayeni uthi wakukhangela ufike ziphelele.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Inzala yakho iya kuba yinyambalala, isizukulwana sakho sinabe njengengca emhlabeni.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Uya kudla ubomi ude ukhokhobe, nqwa nengqolowa engavunwayo lingekafiki ixesha.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Uyabona, siziphicothile ezi zinto, yaye zinjalo; yiva ke, uziqonde ubunyaniso bazo kuwe.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke yena uYobi waphendula wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Akwaba iinkxwaleko zam beziveyishwe kakuhle, iinzingo zam zalinganiswa esikalini.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ubunzima bazo bebuya kudlula nakobentlabathi yaselwandle; ewe, yiyo loo nto amazwi am asuke aba rhabaxa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kaloku iintolo zikaSomandla zindibinzile, ubuhlungu bazo butyhutyh' umzimba; izoyikiso zikaThixo zindiphahlile.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngaba likhe likhonye na iqwarha ikho ingca eluhlaza? Khona, yona inkomo uthi inganxakama zikho iindiza?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Into emtyuba ingatyiwa na ngaphandle kwetyuwa? Inayo na incasa incindi yomxoxozi?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mna ukutya okunjalo andikuchukumisi; ndingathi khe ndayenza loo nto kubuye.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Akwaba uThixo angandiphendula, awufezekise umnqweno wam",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> wokuba uThixo avume ukundixusha, asiyekele isandla sakhe, abunqamle ubomi bam.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Into enjalo ke ingandithuthuzela; ewe, naphakathi kweentlungu ndingavuya ndichulumache, kuba andizange ndaphikisana namazwi alowo uNgcwele.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Ngaba ndisenawo na amandla okuqhubela phambili ndiphila? Khona, siphelo sini sona eso ukuba ndingade ndinyamezele?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bendililitye na kakade? Ngaba ndisisinyithi?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngenene mna ngokwam andisenawo amandla okuzinceda, futhi nempumelelo yam ndiphuncukene nayo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Intlungu yomntu imelwe kukukhathalelwa zizihlobo zakhe, nditsho nokuba yena selekutyeshele ukumhlonela uSomandla.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kambe amawethu anobuqhokolo, afana nentlambo emanzi atshayo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Iba namanzi amdaka anomkhenkce, apho linyibilikela khona ikhephu,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> kodwa lithi lakubalela aphele, lakuba shushu asuke ome qoko!",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Iinqwelo ziyaphambuka endleleni yazo, ziye kuyo, kodwa zifike zife namthanyana kuba kusenkangala.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Iinqwelo zaseTema zikhangela amanzi, nabahambi baseShebha baphunguza benethemba.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kambe ke basuka badane ngenxa yelo themba labo, kuba bathi bakuya kule ntlambo bafike baphoxeke.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Ngoku ke nani ninjalo, kuba nithe nakusibona isibetho endisifumeneyo nasuka nathi rhubaxa noyika.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ngaba ndikhe ndathi kuni: ‘Ndipheni into,’ okanye ndathi: ‘Khanindinyobele ubani ngaloo ndyebo yenu’?",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ngaba ndikhe ndathi: ‘Ndihlanguleni esandleni sotshaba,’ okanye ndathi: ‘Ndihlawuleleni koongalo-nkulu’?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hayi ke, khanindifundise; ndothi cwaka! Ewe, ndiboniseni apho ndiphambuke khona!",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kambe ke wona amazwi athe ngqo aluncedo; ukanti ke ezi ngxoxo zenu ngaba ziphuhlisa ntoni?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ngaba nifuna ukulungisa oko ndikuthethileyo, amazwi omntu oselencamile niwenze intetho engumoya?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Nina nixolele ukwenza amaqashiso nangenkedama, nisenge inzuzo nangesona sihlobo senu.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Kambe ke ngoku khanindijongisise, kuba andisoze ndinixokise ndijongene nani.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ngoku ndiyanithandaza, khanibuyeke ubugqwetha; sanukundisingela phantsi – ndililungisa kule nto.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ngaba nithi kunesikhwa na ukuthetha kwam? Nithi andisakwazi ukwahlukanisa phakathi kokubi nokuhle?”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ke bona ubomi bomntu yimbulaleko emhlabeni; imihla yakhe ngumzabalazo onjengobomi bomqeshwa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Imihla yakhe injengeyekhoboka elisoloko lilangazelela ukuhlwa; injengeyomqeshwa olangazelela umvuzo wakhe.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ewe, esam isabelo ziinyanga ngeenyanga zokulambatha; mna ndabelwe ubusuku beenzingo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Xa ndilalayo ndithi: ‘Yaz'ba kuya kusa nini na?’ Nobo busuku ke busuka bube bude gqitha, ke mna ndibe ndimbola-mboleka kude kuse.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Umzimba wam wambethe iimpethu nothuli; ulusu lona lucandekile, luyabhidla.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Imihla yam ikhawuleza okomatshini wokuluka; iya kufikelela esiphelweni ingaginyisi mathe.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Khawukhumbule ke, kuba ubomi bam bunjengomphunga; amehlo am akasoze aphinde akubone okuhle.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nâbo bandibonayo ngoku soze babe sandibona; ndiya kuphel' emehlweni undijongile.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Njengokuqhabalakana nokunyamalala kwamafu unjalo ofayo, akaphindi abuye.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Akaphindi eze ekhayeni lakhe, angabi sazana nendawo yakhe.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Hayi khona, andiyi kuthi cwaka! Ndiya kuwuphalaza umva-ndedwa wam, ndikhale ndibindekile!",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngani ke ukuba ude undimisele umlindi? Ngaba ndilulwandle, okanye isilo solwandle?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ndakulala ndiye ndicinge ukuba umandlalo wam wondithuthuzela, ndithi ubuthongo bondithomalalisa.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kodwa wena usuka undirhwaqelise ngamaphupha; usuka undivingcele ngemibono.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ndide ke mna ndikhethe ukukrwitshwa; kanye ndinyula ukufa kunokuphila kulo mzimba wam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ewe kambe, ndidikiwe bobu bomi; kakade andiyi kuphila ngonaphakade. Hayi ndiyekeni, kuba ubomi bam bunjengomphunga.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Yaz'ba uyintoni na umntu, le nto umxabise kangaka; ngani ukuba umzondelele kangaka?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ewe, yonke imihla uyamphicotha; ngayo yonke imizuzu uyamvavanya.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hayi kaloku, khawuthi gu kancinci; khawundiyeke ndikhe ndiginy' amathe!",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ke ukuba ndiyona, ikukhathaza ngani loo nto, wena Malusi woluntu? Ngani ukuba ndibe selisweni lakho kangaka? Ngaba ndingumthwalo ongako kuwe?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngaba awungendixoleli na isono sam, ubulibale ubutyala bam? Kuba ke ngoku ndiza kulala kobandayo; uthi undifuna ndibe ndingasekho!”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Waphendula ke uBhildadi umfo waseShuwa, wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Mfondini, koda kube nini ushwaqa, usenza imbudede yamazwi afana nomoya obhudlayo?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Uthi uThixo angakujika okulungileyo? Uthi uSomandla angabugqwetha ubulungisa?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ukuba abantwana bakho bawaphule ummiselo wakhe, yena ke ubawisele isohlwayo esibafaneleyo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Into omawuyenze wena kukuzibika kuThixo, ubuse umbongoze uSomandla.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ukuba ungumntu onyanisekileyo omsulwa, ngenene uya kukuva, akubuyekeze ngomzi wakho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ewe, ubunayo inkqubela ngaphambili, kodwa ayinakulinganiswa nendyebo owoba nayo esiphelweni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Khawuphonononge ulande imbali yemihla yamandulo; phicotha ufunde kumava amanyange.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kaloku thina singabayizolo, asazi nto, nemihla yethu emhlabeni idlula njengesithunzi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ke bona baya kukululeka, bathethe nawe; ewe, bangakuphokozela kuloo vimba wolwazi lwabo, bathi:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ‘Ngaba ingaphuma na imizí apho kungekho mgxobhozo? Uthi ingakhula ingcongolo apho kungekho manzi?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Zithi zingekalungeli kukhiwa, zimbatshe kuqala kunezinye izityalo.’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Iba njalo indlela yabo bonke abamlibalayo uThixo; ewe, ithemba lâbo bangamnquliyo uThixo liyadaka.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kaloku bona bangqiyama ngentambo yesigcawu, lisuke ke elo themba labo linqamke.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bayama ngendlu yesigcawu, ibe ke yona ingaqinanga; babambelela kuyo ngoku yona igqashu-gqashu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bahluma okwesityalo esinamanzi esibethwa yimitha yelanga, sona esinwenwa siphinyele egadini.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Iingcambu zaso zibhijela amatye, zibambelele kuwo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Phofu ke uthi wakusincothula, kungabi sabonakala ukuba sasikhe sakho.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Uyabona, injalo indlela yokukhula kwaso: indawo yaso ithathwa sesinye.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Ewe, uThixo akamlahli umntu othembekileyo, kodwa akangeke azomeleze izandla zabenzi bokubi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngoko ke úya kulubuyisela uncumo emlonyeni wakho, nemilebe yakho ibobotheke yimincili.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ke bona abakuthiyileyo baya kwambathwa lihlazo; kanti ke yona imizi yabakhohlakeleyo iya kubhanga.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke uYobi waphendula wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ewe, ndiyazi ukuba kunjalo; kambe ke umntu angaphumelela njani xa emi enkundleni noThixo?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Noba ungade uzimisele ukuxoxa, awungebi nako ukuphendula nomnye kwiwaka lemibuzo yakhe.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kaloku yena sisilumko esibalaseleyo ngamandla; akukho mntu unokumelana naye aze aphumelele.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kaloku yena neentaba ezi usuka azisiphule zingazi zona; ewe, ngaloo ngqumbo yakhe usuka azibhukuqe.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Yena nomhlaba lo uyawugungxula, neentsika zawo zitsho ziqhaqhazele.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nelanga uthetha nalo litsho lingaphumi, ke zona iinkwenkwezi uzigubungela zitsho zingaveli.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nguye owawatwabululayo amazulu, waza wandolosa phezu kwawo amaza olwandle.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nguye umenzi weendidi zeenkwenkwezi, oozibhere noomakroza, isilimela nomthala wasezantsi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Yena ngumenzi wezinto ezinkulu ezingaphicothekiyo; kanti nemiqondiso yakhe ayinakubalwa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nokuba selegqitha ngakum andinako ukumbona; uthi tshe ndingaqondanga mna.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Khona selengade athathe into, ngubani ongamnqandayo? Akekho nongabuzayo athi: ‘Wenza ntoni ke?’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kaloku uThixo akabuyi ngamva ngengqumbo yakhe; neentshaba zakhe ezazithelela uRahabhi isilo saselwandle wazinyhasha.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Bendingubani ke mna ukuba ndingade ndiphendulane naye? Khona, ndingawazuza phi amazwi okuxoxa naye?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nditsho sendimsulwa, andingeze ndamxoxisa; nto endingayenzayo kukuzibika ndimbongoze uMgwebi wam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nokuba sendizibika kuye, naxa angade andiphendule, anditsho ukuba angakuva ukuzithethelela kwam.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kaloku yena undintlitha ngenzwinini yesaqhwithi, anditsho imivumbo ixananaze ngaphandle kwesizathu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Akandiniki neli lokukhok' umoya ithuba, koko unditsho ndanengcwangu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Xa kuthethwa ngamandla, nguye onawo; xa kuthethwa ngobulungisa, nguye onokundimangalela.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Ndimsulwa ndinjalo, kodwa ndigwetywa kwangumlomo wam. Nangona ndingade ndibe andinabala, yena angandifumana ndinetyala.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ewe, andinabala, kodwa andizibaleli ntweni; nto nje ndikruqukile bobu bomi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kuba kaloku kuyafana; yiyo loo nto ke ndithi: ‘Yena utshabalalisa bonke, abamsulwa ngokunjalo nezaphula-mthetho.’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Isithwakumbe sithi sakuzisa ukufa yena aphoxise ngaso isibetho sabamsulwa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ihlabathi lisezandleni zezikhohlakali; ke bona abagwebi ubamfamekisile. Xa ingenguye ke uthi ngaba ngubani?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Imihla yam ikhawuleza ngaphezu kwembaleki; ewe, ibaleka gqitha, ibe ke ayinayo nanto incomekayo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Iphala njengesikhephe seengcongolo; ikhawuleza ngathi lukhozi lurhiwula ixhoba.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Noba sendisithi: ‘Hayi, ngoku ndiza kukhe ndizingcwabe izikhalazo zam, ndibobotheke ndihlale ndizonwabele,’",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ndisuka ndoyike ndibe namanwele, kuba ndiyaqonda ukuba wena akungeke undibalele njengongenatyala.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ke, ukuba ndiza kugwetywa, ngani ukuba ndibe sazabalaza?",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Noba ndingade ndihlambe ngekhephu, izandla zam ndizicoce ngesephu,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> wena uya kundiphosa emhadini, nditsho ndibe rhono-rhono, kwankqu neempahla zam zingandamkeli.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Ebengumntu na kakade ukuba ndibe ndiphendulane naye? Hayi, bendingeze ndime naye enkundleni!",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kaloku phakathi kwethu sobabini akukho mlamli unokusahlula ngezandla zakhe.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hayi bo! Khawumke noswazi lwakho khon' ukuze ndingabi sankwantya ndisoyika isohlwayo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Xa kunjalo ke ndingatsho ndithethe ndingenaloyiko, kodwa ngale ndlela izinto zimi ngayo ngoku andinako.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Kwowu, ndidikiwe bobu bomi! Ngoko ke ndosuka ndithethe utyhatyhiwe, isikhalo sam ndisitsho ndibindekile!",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ewe, ndiya kuthetha naye ndithi: ‘Ngani ukuba undigwebe, Thixo? Hayi kaloku, ndazise ityala kuqala.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ikunceda ntoni wena ingcinezelo enje, ukutshabalalisa umsebenzi wezandla zakho, uze uthelele amacebo ezikhohlakali?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngaba amehlo akho afana nawabantu na? Ngaba nawe ubona njengomntu?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngaba imihla yakho ifana neyomntu? Ngaba iminyaka yakho ifana neyakhe na?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngani ke ukuba ugqogqe iziphoso zam, uzingelane nesono sam?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kaloku uyazi ukuba andinatyala, ibe ke futhi uyazi ukuba akekho ongandihlangulayo esandleni sakho.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “ ‘Ndenziwa nguwe nje, ndabunjwa zizandla zakho, ngaba ngoku uza kujika unditshabalalise?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Khumbula kaloku ukuba wandibumba njengodongwe! Ngaba ke ngoku uza kundivuthulula ndibe luthuli?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Andithi na kaloku wandithulula njengobisi, ndaza ke ndakhanywa njengengqaka?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kaloku wandibumba ngamathambo nemisipha, wandinxibisa inyama, wandambathisa ufele.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Wandinika ubomi, wandambesa ngezibele; undinonophele ke wandixhasa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “ ‘Kambe ke zonke ezi zinto undifihlele, kuba le ibiyinjongo yakho kakade.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kaloku wena ube ugade ukuba ndone ukuze undigwebe ngenxa yesono sam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ukuba ke ndisisikhohlakali kunyembelekile kum! Kambe ke noba ndililungisa andinaqhayiya, kuba ndibandezelekile, ndambethwe lihlazo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Noba ndingade ndiqholose wena ungandizingela njengengonyama, uphinde wenze kum ngokwaloo mandla akho amangalisayo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Usoloko unamangqina andintywiliselayo, ibe ke nengqumbo yakho iyakhula ngakum, kuba uyaphindelela ukundihlasela.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “ ‘Kwakutheni ukuze undiyeke ndizalwe? Awu! Akwaba ndandife ndingekalanywa naliliso eli!",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ngoku ngendifana nongazange abekho, kuba ngendavela nje ndasiwa engcwabeni.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ewe, bufutshane kambe ubomi bam! Hayi khona, khawundiyeke ndikhe ndiphumle kancinane!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kaloku ngoku ndiyahamba, ibe ke soze ndibuye; ndiya kwilizwe lethunzi nobumnyama.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ewe, ndiya kwilizwe lobumnyama namathunzi, nelesithokothoko sobumnyama, apho ukukhanya kufana nobumnyama.’ ”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke uZofare waseNama waphendula wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Uthi kungathi cwaka, ingaphendulwa le nyambalala yamazwi akho? Ucinga ukuba ukulavuza okunje kungamthethelela umntu?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Uthi oku kubhobhoza kwakho kuya kusenza sithi cwaka? Uthi wena ngoku uphoxisa thina masikuyeke singakuphoxi?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Andithi na kaloku wena uthi imfundiso yakho imsulwa, nawe ngokwakho awunabala phambi koThixo?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Awu, akwaba uThixo ebengadandulukayo athethe nawe,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> akhe akubonise iingontsi-ngontsi zobulumko! Kuba kambe kunzulu ukwazi kwakhe! Yiqonde into yokuba esi sohlwayo akunike sona uThixo siyalaba-laba kubutyala bakho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Uthi ungahle uziqonde iingontsi-ngontsi zobunzulu bukaThixo, ngokunjalo nobungakanani bamandla kaSomandla?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hayi bo, úngaphaya kwakho, namazulu uwakrobele! Ewe, yena ubona nelabafileyo, ube ke wena awazi nto!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> UThixo ulivelele ihlabathi, kanti ke ulukrobele nolwandle!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ukuba ke usuka akubambe edlula, aze akuse ematyaleni, ngubani ongamnqandayo?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kaloku yena uyabazi oongantweni; ke, xa ebona ububi ùthi makangenzi nto?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ke zona iziyatha zoza zibe nengqondo mhla iqwarha lazala umntu!",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Ukuba uthe wayisebenzisa ingqondo yakho, unganako ukolulela izandla kuThixo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ukuba uphethe ububi yahlukana nabo, nezinto zenkohlakalo mazingafumaneki nasemzini wakho.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ukuba unokwenjenjalo ke unganako ukuma ungenaxhala nganto, ume ngxishi ungenadyudyu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngako ke ungatsho uyilibale yonke le mbandezelo; ewe, ilibaleke njengeempuphuma zomlambo oseluwuthile.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ke bona ubomi bakho buya kutsho buqaqambe ngathi kusemin' emaqanda. Le meko yakho yokubandezeleka ijike ibe yeginyis' amathe, oku komsobomvu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Uya kutsho uzithembe, kuba kaloku nekamva liqaqambile. Ngenene uya kuhlala ukhuselekile ungenaxhala.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Uya kuthi zava ungenadyudyu, bathi nabaninzi bacele uncedo kuwe.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ke zona izikhohlakali ziya kucinywa amehlo, abe ke namathuba okuphuncula engasekho, kuphela kwanto iseleyo kukuqhawuka.”"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke uYobi waphendula wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Inene, ningabona bantu; ibe ke nobulumko buya kufa nani!",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kambe ke nam ndinengqondo njengani; anindidluli nganto. Kakade ke nithi ngubani ongàzaziyo ezi zinto?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Mna ndiyakhala kuThixo, aze andiphendule; kodwa ngoku sendiyintlekisa nakwizihlobo zam – ewe, ilungisa lomfo ongenabala, kambe ke namhlanje ndisisigculelo!",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Oseshweni uyadelwa ngabathe zava; ogxadazelayo uyakhatywa!",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kukho ulonwabo ezindlwini zezikrelemnqa; abamqumbisayo uThixo bakhuselekile; nditsho abo bacingayo ukuba uThixo usezandleni zabo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Kodwa ke khanibuze nakwiinyamakazi, ziya kunifundisa; nibuze nasezintakeni, zinixelele.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Khaningqawe ulwazi nakwizilo zomhlaba, ziya kuninika; ninkinkqe ukuqonda nasezintlanzini elwandle, ziya kuniphokozela.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Phakathi kwazo akukho ungaqondiyo ukuba le nto yenziwe *nguNdikhoyo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kaloku zonke izinto eziphilayo zisesandleni sakhe, nobomi boluntu lonke buxhomekeke kuye.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kaloku kwanjengokuba umlomo usiva ubunjani bokutya, nendlebe ke iyawaphicotha amazwi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ubulumko buyafumaneka kwiingwevu; ke bona ubudala buza namava.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Kanti ke yena uThixo unobulumko namandla, amacebo nengqiqo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Into ayiqhaqhileyo akukho mntu unokubuya ayakhe; ngokunjalo nomntu amvaleleyo akukho ungamvulelayo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> UThixo akuwavalela amanzi kuyabalela; kanti ke akuwavulela kutsho kube ziimpuphuma.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ukomelela noloyiso lolwakhe, kanti ke nabakhohlisi ngokunjalo nabakhohliswa basesandleni sakhe.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Yena amaphakathi uwatsho ancitheke, nabagwebi abatsho babe ziimpanga-mpanga.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Uyawakhulula amakhamandela aqhotyoshwe ngookumkani, aze bona ngokwabo abanxibise umbhinqo wamabanjwa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ababingeleli ubatsho baphoxeke, aze wona amakhwahla awakhiqe.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Amaciko athenjiweyo uwatsho abhibhidle; aze ayiphuthise nengqiqo yamadoda amakhulu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Amatshawe uwahlaza ngendelelo; ke zona iingwanyalala uzihlutha izixhobo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Utyhila izinto ezifihlakele ezinzulwini zobumnyama, nobona bumbonde-mbonde abujike bube kukukhanya.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Uyazikhulisa izizwe, abuye azivuthulule; azithi jize ngobungangalala, abuye aziyekele zithinjwe.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Iinkokheli zezizwe uzitsho zibe zizithwanga-thwanga, zifathule zibhadula enkangala.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ngoko ke ziphutha-phutha ebumnyameni, kungekho kukhanya; zigxadazele njengamanxila."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Hayi kaloku, zonke ezi zinto sendikhe ndazibona ngala wam amehlo; ewe, ndizivile ngezi zam iindlebe, ndaye ke ndiziqonda.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Zonke ezi zinto nizaziyo nam ndiyazazi; anindidlule nganto.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kambe ke mna okunokwam ndifuna ukuthetha noSomandla, ndiwaneke ndiwuxoxe naye lo mcimbi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ke nina nilibele kukugquma inyaniso ngobuxoki; nifana nqwa neqithilili logqirha ongenakunyanga mntu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Akwaba beningathi cwaka; oko kuthula kwenu bekungaba bobona bulumko benu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Khaniphulaphule xa ndixoxayo, nive ukuzithethelela kwam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nicinga ukuba ningakuThixo, nide nikhuthaze intswela-bulungisa nje? Nithi ninceda yena ngale nkohliso?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ngaba nizama ukuthatha icala ngenxa yakhe? Nifuna ukuthethela uThixo?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nithi kunganjani xa anokuthi anigoca-goce? Mhlawumbi naye nithi ningamkhohlisa ngale ndlela nibakhohlisa ngayo abantu?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Inene, uya kunohlwaya, ukuba nenza isheyi ngokufihlakeleyo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ewe, ubungangamsha bakhe buya kunirhwaqelisa, nonganyelwe kukunkwantya.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kaloku ezi zangotshe zenu zifana nelahle elinothuthu; zaye ke nezi ngxoxo zenu ziya kusumka ngathi ludongwe.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Sukan' apha! Khanindiyeke ndithethe utyhatyhiwe, yehl' ehlayo!",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ngoku ndiza kuzibeka esichengeni, ubomi bam bube semngciphekweni.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Noba selengade andigwinte andikhathali; kodwa ukuxoxa oku ke kona ndiza kuxoxa, ndiyandlale kuThixo imeko yam!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Mhlawumbi le nto yeyona ingandisindisayo, kuba ke akukho saphula-mthetho singade sibe nokujongana naye.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Khanibaz' iindlebe nindiphulaphule, niyiqwalasele ingcaciso yam.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hayi ke, ngoku sendiqule ndaligangatha; futhi ndiza kuyibeka imeko yam, ndixoxe ndiphume phambili.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ngaba ukhona na ongabambana nam? Kuba xa kunjalo ndothi cwaka ndife.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Masivumelane ngezi zinto zimbini, Thixo, ukuze ndingabi sazama kuzifihla kuwe.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Sirhoxise kum isandla sakho, sahlukane nam; mandingabi sahlala ndirhwaqele ndisoyika wena.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Uze uthethe, ndiya kukuphendula; okanye kuya kuthetha mna, ke wena uze undiphendule.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bungakanani na ubugwenxa bam nesono sam? Ndazise ubutyala nokona kwam.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngani ukuba undifulathele, undithathe njengotshaba?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ngoku sowusukelisana negqabi eliphephethekayo? Uhlasela inkintshi-nkintshi yomququ?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kaloku undimangalela ngezityholo ezinzima; ude undityabeke ngobutyala bam basebuntwaneni.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Iinyawo zam uzikhonkxa ngezikhuni; uyazigqala zonke iindlela zam, uzicandele umda iintende zeenyawo zam.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ngenxa yoko ndivuthuluka njengevithi; sendifana nempahla edliwe ngamanundu.”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Hayi kambe umntu, intw' ezelwe ngumfazi! Mifutshane imihla yakhe; izele ziinkathazo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Uvela njengentyatyambo, akhawuleze abune; uthi tshe oku kwesithunzi, aphel' emehlweni.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Uthi onjalo ke ungamgqala, ude ume naye enkundleni umgwebe?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngaba ukhona na ongakhupha into ehlambulukileyo kwengahlambulukanga? Unotshe, akukho namnye!",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kaloku imihla yakhe seyimisiwe, nenani leenyanga zakhe liyaziwa nguwe; kananjalo ke ummisele umda angenakuwutsiba.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Somyeka, ungabi samjonga, akhe aphumle njengomqeshwa ogqibe umsebenzi wemini.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Umthi xa ugawuliwe lisekhona ithemba ngawo; awunakufa kuphele, usenokubuya uhlume amagqabi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Noba ingakhula ibe ndala ingcambu yawo emhlabeni nesiphunzi sawo sife apho simile khona,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> uthi nje ukuba ukhe wasezela ukunyepha kwamanzi, utsho uhlume, uvelise amasebe njengegatyana lomthi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ukanti ke yena umntu uyafa, iphel' intw' ibithethwa. Ewe, uyafa aphel' emehlweni.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Njengokuba amanzi echibi ephela, namanzi omlambo esitsha ome;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> nomntu ke unjalo, ulala phantsi angabuyi avuke. Ibe ke soze aphinde avuke, okanye ashukunyiswe kobo buthongo bakhe, ade amazulu angabi sabikho.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Akwaba ubungandifihla kwelo labafileyo ide ithothe ingqumbo yakho, uze ke undimisele ixesha oya kundikhumbula ngalo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ukuba ngaba ke umntu ufile, angabuya aphile? Xa kunjalo ngendilinda yonke imihla yokubulaleka kwam, lide lifike ixesha lokukhululeka kwam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngewundibiza, ndisabele ke mna, kuba wena ukulangazelela ukubona umsebenzi wezandla zakho.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngewuzibala izinyathelo zam, ungaziqwalaseli noko iziphoso zam.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Zonke izikreqo zam ziya kuvalelwa engxoweni, ubugqume ubugwenxa bam.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kodwa wena uyalitshitshisa ithemba lomntu, oku kweentaba ezidilikayo zivuthuluke, oku kwamawa asunduziweyo angabi sabakho, nditsho oku kwamanzi awadlayo amatye, okwezandyondyo zemvula eziwukhukulisayo umhlaba.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Umntu umvikiva kube kanye, angabi sabikho; uguqula ubuso bakhe, umgxothe.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Oonyana bakhe noba sebewongekile, akaqondi yena; ukanti akaboni naxa sebehlazeka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kaloku into emdlayo yintlungu yesiqu sakhe, abe ezililela yena buqu.”"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke uElifazi waseTeman waphendula wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Uthi isilumko singaze sitsho ngembudede enje? Singathi kanti sihlalele ukubhodla umoya wasempuma?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Wawusibona phi isilumko esibhibhidla kanje xa sixoxayo, esisuka sizithethelele ngamazwi ayimfeketho njengawe lo?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Wena ngoku uyakuphuthisa ukuthobela uThixo; ngale ndlela yakho akukho bani ongaphinda anxulumane noThixo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ukuthetha kwakho sekulawulwa bubugwenxa; ulwimi lwakho luvuza amaqhinga.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Wena awugwetywa nandim, koko ngumlomo wakho, ngamazwi akho kanye akugwebayo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Nguwe na umntu wokuqala ukuzalwa? Ngaba wavela kungekabikho neentaba ezi?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ngaba wawukho kwigqugula likaThixo? Ngani ke ukuba ububange kangaka ubulumko?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Zinto zini ezi zaziwa nguwe wedwa singazaziyo thina? Ngaba kukho izinto eziyintsonkotha ezicace kuwe wedwa?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Thina sineengwevu namadoda amakhulu, amadala nditsho nakuyihlo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kutheni ukuba unganeli yintuthuzelo kaThixo, okanye ngala mazwi sikubongoza ngawo?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Yintoni le ikulahlekisa kangaka? Atshawuziswa yintoni amehlo akho?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kutheni ukuba uvukelane noThixo, ude uthethe amazwi anje?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Nguwuphi umntu ongade abe nyulu, ingubani kwabazelweyo ngabafazi ongafumaneka engenatyala?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Khumbula kaloku ukuba uThixo akathembanga nditsho neengcwele zakhe zasezulwini; ewe, nezulu ngokwalo alikho nyulu emehlweni akhe.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ubeka phi ke yena umntu eyinto elisikizi ephuthileyo nje? Kuxa engubani esela uluchwe lobubi nje oku kwamanzi?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Khawuphulaphule ndikhe ndikuxelele, ndikwazise izinto endizibonileyo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nditsho ezo zaxelwayo zizilumko njengoko zona zingafihlelwanga ngamanyange.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kaloku wona eli lizwe alinikwa laba lelawo odwa kungekho maveza-ndlebe.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Isikhohlakali sihlala sibhinyalaza singcungcutheka yonke imihla yaso; ewe, bunjalo ke bonke ubomi bomntu ongqwabalala!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kaloku sisoloko sisothuswa yingxolo esezindlebeni zaso; size sihlaselwe xa sizicingela ukuba sikhuselekile.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Asinathemba lakuphuncula ebumnyameni kuba sihleli silindelwe likrele.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kaloku lo mntu usesichengeni sokuba kukutya kwamaxhalanga; uqonda kakuhle ukuba yintshabalalo ngaphambili.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Usuka onganyelwe yinkxwaleko nomva-ndedwa, kanye oku kokumkani esiya kuhlasela.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kaloku yena usolulele kuThixo isandla sakhe, wazenza igorha kuSomandla,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> emhlasela engakhathalele, ephethe elo khaka lakhe elingqingqwa.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Noxa ubuso bakhe bugutyungelwe ngamanqatha, nemihlubulo yakhe ivuthelene kukutyeba,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> izixeko zakhe ziya kuba ngamanxuwa; indlu yakhe ilil' ibhungane; ngokukhawuleza iza kuba ngamabhodlo nje.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ewe, uya kuphelelwa kukuba sisityebi, ize nendyebo yakhe ibhange, nditsho nenzuzo yakhe ingabi sabakho kulo lonke ilizwe.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Akayi kubuphepha ubumnyama bokufa. Ihlumelo lakhe liya kurhawulwa lilangatye, amazwi akhe aphephetheke nomoya.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Makangazikhohlisi aqamele ngamampunge, kuba inzuzo yakhe iya kuba lilize.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Uya kutshazwa phambi kwexesha, amagqabi angaze abe luhlaza.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Uya kufana nomdiliya ovuthuluke iziqhamo ziseluhlaza, nqwa nomnquma ovuthuluke iintyatyambo.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Lonke elo qela labangamnquliyo uThixo aliyi kuba nanto, nemizi yabo eyakhiwe ngezinyobo iya kuvuthululwa ngumlilo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kaloku bakhawula ububi, bazale uqhushululu, inzala yabo ibe yinkohliso.”"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke uYobi waphendula wenjenje:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Zonke ezi zinto nindixelela zona sendikhe ndaziva ngaphambili; inene, xa ninonke ningabathuthuzeli abangento.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngaba le ntshwaqane yenu ayinasiphelo? Nomelezwa yintoni kangaka engxoxweni?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nam bendingathethayo ngolo hlobo xa ibinini abakule meko ndikuyo; bendiya kuthetha nani ndimana ndichan' amagama, ndide ndimane ndihlunguzela intloko.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bendiya kunomeleza ngamacebiso, ndinithuthuzele ngamazwi alalanisayo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Kambe ke, nokuba ndiyathetha, intlungu le ayisuki; kanti ke nokuba ndithule, kusafana.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hayi ke, ngoku uThixo undiqobile; usapho lwam uluvuthulule bhuqe!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ndifunyenwe nguye, kwaza oko kwaba bubungqina bokundityhola; ukonakala komzimba wam bubungqina obundidobelelayo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngale ngqumbo yakhe undiqwengile wandenzakalisa; undisinekele ngaloo mazinyo akhe; yena mchasi wam uyandijamela.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Abantu bathetha ngam bendigxeka; bandimpakaza esidleleni ngengcikivo, bebonke badibana ngokundichasa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> UThixo undiyekele ngezaphula-mthetho, wandinikela ezandleni zezikhohlakali.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Mna bendingacingele nto, suka ke yena wandintlekeza, wandibamba ngobhongwana, wandiqwenga. Ewe, mna sendiyeyona nto ajolise kuyo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Abeentolo bakhe bandirhawule; undincule izintso engenalusini, wayiphalazela emhlabeni inyongo yam.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Undingxwelerhe wada wandiqusha; ufunzela kum okwejoni.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Ngoku sendithe wambu ezokuzila; uphondo lwam luseluthulini.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Sendilile ndada ndambatsha; ke wona amehlo am ade af' amnyama.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kambe ke phofu mna andinabundlongo-ndlongo, nomthandazo wam kuThixo awunakumbi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Yini na, mhlaba! Sukulingcwab' igazi lam! Isikhalo sam masivakale!",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kaloku nangoku ingqina lam lisemazulwini; ewe, ukho ongakum ondithethelelayo kweliphezulu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sendiyintlekisa nakwizihlobo zam; ke iinyembezi zam ndiziphalaza phambi koThixo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Akwaba ebenokulamla phakathi komntu noThixo njengoko ebakho umlamli phakathi komntu nomhlobo wakhe!",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kuba kaloku akuseminyaka mingaphi ndithathe uhambo olungabuyiyo.”"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Umoya wam wonakele, nemihla yam iphelile; ngoku sending'ong'ozelwe lingcwaba.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Inene, ngapha nangapha ndiphahlwe ngabandigculelayo; ewe, ndijongene nentiyo yabo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Nceda, Thixo, undibekele isibambiso. Kakade ke ibingubani omnye ongandikhuselayo?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kaloku iingqiqo zabo uzithe lwale ngokungaqondi; ngoko ke mabangandoyisi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kaloku umntu ongcothoza izihlobo zakhe ngenxa yenzuzo, abantwana bakhe baya kufa amehlo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Undenze ndaba ngundaba-mlonyeni kubantu bonke, into etshicelwa ebusweni.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngenxa yeenzingo amehlo am selede anorhatyazo; sendide ndayingcadalala ephephukayo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Abo banyanisekileyo ke bamangalisiwe; ewe, abamsulwa bayakhathazeka ngenxa yabachasene noThixo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Olilungisa ubambelele nkqi endleleni yakhe, ngokunjalo ke nabo bazandla zimsulwa baya besomelela ngokomelela.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Kambe ke, noba niyaphinda nibuye xa ninonke, andiyi kufumana nasinye isilumko apho phakathi kwenu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Imihla yam iphelile, namacebo am achithakele, ngokunjalo neminqweno yam ivuthulukile.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ubusuku bathi yimini; kanti xa kuhlwayo bathi sekuza kusa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Uthi ke, xa ndingasuka ndithi elabafileyo likhaya lam, ndize ndizandlalele kwamnyama-ndawo,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> okanye ke, xa ndinokuthi ingcwaba ngubawo, ndize ndithi iimpethu ngumama nodade wethu:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> liphi ke ithemba lam, ingubani khona onokundibonelela?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngaba bendinokuhla nalo na ndiye emasangweni elabafileyo? Bendinokuhla nalo na, ndiye kuphumla nalo eluthulini?”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kwesi sithuba ke kuthathise uBhildadi, umfo waseShuwa, wenjenje:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Koda kube nini untyuntya? Hayi bo, khawubuyel' ezingqondweni, nathi ke sithethe!",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kutheni ukuba usiphathe okwezilwanyana? Ngaba usibona siziziyatha ezinjalo?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Uyazenzakalisa ngalo msindo wakho. Ngaba umhlaba mawujike ube yinkangala ukungqinela ukunyaniseka kwakho? Uthi makudilik' amawa ezindaweni zawo?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Hayi kaloku, isibane sesikhohlakali siza kucinywa, futhi ke nelangatye laso soze liphinde livuthe.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ukukhanya kuya kujika kube bubumnyama endlwini yaso; ewe, isibane saso siya kucinywa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Siza kuphelelwa kukunyantsula, sikhutyekiswe kwalelaso iqhinga.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Iinyawo zaso ziya kugaxeleka kwisabatha, size sigxalathelane siye kuthi gxwa emhadini.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Umgibe wosuka usithi hlasi ngesithende, usiqhoge usibambe ntshilikithi!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kaloku sibekelwe isabatha emhlabeni, sacutshelwa unoxhaka endleleni yaso.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Lo mntu urhwaqeliswa zizoyikiso ngeenxa zonke; zimthe mbende zimpheka zimophula.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Inkxwaleko imlambele; uhlala ezingelwa sisithwakumbe.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Uthiwe mome sisifo esilenceza ulusu lwakhe; ewe, kanye izibulo lokufa limgrenya amalungu omzimba.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Woqwengelwa apho kwelo nqugwala liyinqaba yakhe, suka ukufa kumqweqwedisele kwikumkani yezoyikiso.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Akukho nto iyeyakhe iya kusala kwelo nqugwala lakhe; kaloku isulfure evuthayo iya kusasazeka phezu kwalo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Phants' apha iingcambu zakhe ziya koma, kanti ke wona amasebe akhe atshaze phezulu phaya.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Udumo lwakhe luya kutshitsha elizweni, negama lakhe lilibaleke ehlabathini.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Wogxothwa kweli lizwe lokukhanya, akhatshelwe ebumnyameni; ewe, uya kunikw' uphum' aphele kwelimiweyo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Akayi kushiya mlibo nanzala phakathi kwamawabo; ngenene akayi kushiya nempunde le kwelakowabo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Abasentshona bothi bakuyiva le ntlekele bakhamnqe; kanti ke abasempuma bothi bakuva ngesi sibetho batsho babamb' ongezantsi!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kuya kuba njalo ke kwindlu yesikhohlakali. Ewe, injalo indawo yongamkhathalelanga uThixo!”"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku waphendula uYobi wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Yaz'ba koda kube nini na nindingcungcuthekisa, nindaphula nindikroboza ngamazwi?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kunini niphoxisa ngam! Aninantloni ukundihlasela kangaka?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Khona sekusithiwa ndonile, ningena phi ke nina?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Eyona nto ngoku niyandivuyelela; kuni ezi nkathazo zam zibonisa ubutyala bam.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Anisaboni ke nina ukuba nguThixo lo undifake kule ngxingwa? Ewe kaloku, nguye ondigubungele ngomnatha.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Ndiba ngakhwaza ndisithi: ‘Ugonyamelo!’ andifumani nokuhoywa oku! Futhi ndibe ngazibika, akukho bani undilamlelayo!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Yena uyivalile indlela yam ukuze ndingabi nakugqitha. Iindlela zam uzithe zinzi ngobumnyama.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Yena undihlube iwonga lam, wandihlutha naloo ntshinga bendinayo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Undidilize macal' onke, ndee shwaka, walincothula njengomthi ithemba lam.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ingqumbo yakhe uyijolise kum; undiphethe njengolona tshaba lwakhe.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Undikhuphele umkhosi wakhe; undimbela izikanisi zokundihlasela; ujikeleza umzi wam.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Unditsho ndabalekwa nangabantakwethu; xa kungokunje nezihlobo zam ezi zihambela phaya!",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Okwakuzizalamane zam zindishiyile, ngokunjalo nabazalana nam bandilibele.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Abo babeziindwendwe zam abasandikhumbuli, nezicakazana zam azisandazele nto, sendithathwa njengowasemzini.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ndakusibiza isicaka sam, asisabeli nokusabela oku, nditsho nokuba ndiyasicenga.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kanti nomfazi wam weenkomo selekhutyekiswa kukuphefumla kwam; sendiliqaqa nakwabesizalo sikama.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Sendidelwe nangabantwana aba bembala; bathi ndakuthi gqi bakrukrutheke yintsini.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Endandikade ndilala ngengub' enye nabo, bayandicaphukela; ukanti nâbo ndibathandayo bandivukele.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Izihlunu zam sezithe nca emathanjeni, nolusu lwam sendilonwaya ngamazinyo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Hoyina! Hoyina, balingane bam; khanibe nebuya-mbo! Kaloku sisandla sikaThixo esi sindenze ndanje!",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ngani ukuba nani ninditshutshise njengoThixo? Hayi kaloku, noko ngoku sekwanele!",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Akwaba ebekho owabhalayo la mazwi am; akwaba ebeshicilelwe encwadini!",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngenene akwaba la mazwi ebekrolwe elityeni ngentsimbi ebukhali nangelothe, khon' ukuze ahlale ehleli nanini nanini!",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kambe ke ndiyazi ukuba umkhululi wam ukho; ekugqibeleni iya kuba nguye otshatshelayo ehlabathini.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Nokuba ulusu lwam lungade ludlavulwe sesi sifo, noko uThixo yena ndiya kumbona ndidlavuke ndinjalo!",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ewe, ndiya kumbona ngala wam amehlo, indim, ingenguye wumbi. Loo nto ndiyilangazelela ngomxhelo wam wonke.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ke nina nisuka nithi: ‘Hayi ukungcungcutheka kwakhe! Yabe ingcambu yaloo nto ikuye ngenkqu.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kambe ke lilumkeleni ikrele elifunza kuni, ikrele lengqumbo kaThixo ngenxa yesono; liya kunenza niqonde ukuba ukhona umgwebi.”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku uZofare waseNama waphendula wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ukudubeka kwam kundibangela ukuba mandiphendule; kunditsho ndikungxamele ukuthetha.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngale ndlela undigxeka ngayo uyandihlaza, kodwa ndiza kukuphendula ngengqiqo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngaba akuyiqondi le nto, ingathi lisiko lidala nje? Laqala kwaukufika komntu wokuqala ehlabathini.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nditsho le nto yokuba ulonwabo lwesikhohlakali alubhekele phi. Kaloku imincili yalowo ungamnquliyo uThixo yeyomzuzwana nje.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ewe, yena angasisihandiba esiwakrobeleyo namazulu, abe sisikhulu esintloko irheca amafu,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> kodwa wosuka adake kuphele njengelindle lakhe, baze abo bebembonile bathi: ‘Utshone phi na?’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Usuka athi shwaka njengephupha, azimele njengombono wasebusuku, angaze aphinde alanywe bani.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ababehlala bembona abaphindi bambone, futhi nendawo yakhe ingaze ibe samalama.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Abantwana bakhe baya kubabuyekeza abasweleyo, izandla zakhe zibuyisele ubutyebi bakhe kubo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nakuba wayefudula enamandla ngeemini zobutsha bakhe, kodwa ngoku loo mandla aya kulala eluthulini kunye naye.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Inkohlakalo inganambitheka kamnandi emlonyeni wakhe, ade ayigushe phantsi kolwimi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Anganamathela kuyo angavumi ukwahlukana nayo, asuke akhethe ukuhlala eyimumathile ngenkalakahla.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kodwa ke oko kutya kwakhe esiswini sakhe kosuka kukrakre, kube ngathi yityhefu yephimpi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kaloku umntu okhohlakeleyo ubutyebi ubuginya ajike abuhlanze; uThixo ubugrumba nakweso sisu sakhe.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Isikhohlakali simfimfitha ubuhlungu bamaphimpi, buze busibinze kanye oku kobuhlungu berhamba.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Asihlali side sibone imilambo empompoza amanzi, okanye iintlambo ezinkcenkceza ubusi namasi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ukubulaleka kwaso kufuneka sikuncame singakhange sikuxhamle; kaloku asilifumani ithuba lokubutya ubutyebi baso, sinambithe imveliso yokurhweba kwaso.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Andithi na kaloku sona saphila kukucinezela abahlelelekileyo; izindlu sizifumana singazakhanga?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Kaloku ukunyoluka komntu okhohlakeleyo akunasiphelo; ulixhoba leminqweno yakhe.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Utya konke, angashiyi nto; ngoko ke ngoku inkqubela yakhe isuke yanqamka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Uthi xa asencotsheni yempumelelo ahlelwe ziinzima; zisuke zimfikele ngamandla iinkathazo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Angatya yena ahluthe mpu, kodwa uThixo wosuka amnisele ngengqumbo yakhe, amohlwaye ngokumzisela imfazwe.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Xa azama ukuphepha ikrele elenziwe ngentsimbi uya kuchanwa lutolo lobhedu, lumbinze luphumele.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Xa elikhupha emqolo, encothula intloko yalo ekhazimlayo enyongweni, wosuka onganyelwe kukunkwantya.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Yonke indyebo yakhe yovuthuluka iphele, kuthi gqi umlilo ongaphenjwanga mntu utshabalalise okushiyekileyo endlwini yakhe.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Amazulu osuka awadandalazise amatyala akhe, ke lona ihlabathi lisuke limvukele.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Indlu yakhe iya kukhukuliswa, imke nomsinga wamanzi ngemini yengqumbo kaThixo.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Naso ke isabelo uThixo asinika abakhohlakeleyo; ewe, elo lilifa abamisele lona uThixo.”"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> UYobi ke waphendula wenjenje:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Khanibek' iindlebe nindiphulaphule; leyo ke yoba yeyona ntuthuzelo kum.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Khanindinyamezele nam ndikhe ndithethe; emva koko ke ningaqhubela phambili niphoxise.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Ke mna ndifanele ukukhathazeka; kaloku andixabananga nomntu nje.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Jongani kum: niya kumangaliswa, nibamb' ongezantsi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nam ndithi ndakuyicinga le nto indihleleyo ndisuke ndikhwankqiswe, ndize ndifikelwe kukungcangcazela komzimba.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngani ukuba abakhohlakeleyo bayizuze inyhweba yokukhula bade babe badala, baxhamle ukomelela nenkqubela?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bakhula babe nabantwana nabazukulwana; ewe, baba nenyhweba yokusibukela isizukulwana sabo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Emizini yabo bonwabile, abakhathazwa nto; uThixo akabayekeli ngezibetho.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kubo iinkunzi ziyazizalisa iimazi, zingashiyi nanye; ibe ke neemazi zabo ziyazala zingaphunzi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Owabo umlisela utaka-taka ngokwamatakane; abantwana babo bayadloba-dloba.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ungafika bememelela bekhatshwa ziintambula neengqongqo; bangqungqa benemincili bebetha iifluthi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Obabo ubomi babudla ngentlutha nenzolo, baze bathi nyubelele baye kutshona kwelemimoya ngaphandle kwamagingxi-gingxi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Izikhohlakali zithi kuThixo: ‘Suka kuthi! Asinamdla wakuzazi iindlela zakho.’",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Zisuka zithi: ‘Kuxa engubani yena uSomandla ukuba singade simbuse? Khona, nzuzoni esiyifumanayo ngokumnqula?’",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kambe impumelelo yazo ayixhomekekanga ezandleni zazo. Mna andihambisani necebo lâbo bantu bakhohlakeleyo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Kukangaphi isibane sesikhohlakali sicinywa? Kukangaphi zingundaniselwa zizibetho? Andithi na kaloku uThixo abakhohlakeleyo ubahlomlela ingqumbo yakhe,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> aze abavuthele baphephetheke njengengca enqunqiweyo, bavuthuluke njengomququ unyuka nesaqhwithi?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ngaba uThixo usibekela abantwana isohlwayo sabazali? Hayi bo; makohlwaye abo bonileyo ngokwabo, khon' ukuze nabo baqonde.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Abo bonileyo mabaxhamle isohlwayo, basele ingqumbo kaSomandla.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kakade ke, umntu uwukhathalele ngani umzi wakhe xa yena engasekho, xa iinyanga zakhe azibalelweyo kobu bomi seziphelile?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Ngubani ongafundisa uThixo ulwazi? Nezithwala-ndwe zaphezulu zisesandleni sakhe nje!",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bambi bafa bethe gabhu kwintlala-kahle nenkqubela; bafa bengazele nto bekhuselekile.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ewe, bafikelwa kukufa iimvaba zabo zizele ngamasi; nangokwasempilweni bayimiqaba-qaba.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ukanti ke bambi bafa benxunguphele, bengazange bayive nokuyiva intlala-kahle.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kambe ke bonke bayafa bangcwatywe, baze ke babe lixhoba leempethu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ewe, ndiyakubona ukuyila kweengqiqo zenu, ngokunjalo naloo mayelenqe niwayilayo ukuchasana nam.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Niyawaza kubuza ke nithi: ‘Uphi umzi wesikhulu xa kunamhlanje-nje? Iphi loo ndlu sasiyenzela kuyo inkohlakalo?’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ngaba anikhe nibuze na kwabalikhenkethileyo ilizwe? Ke, ngaba anikayiqondi ingxelo yabo?",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Le yokuba ngomhla wesithwakumbe isikhohlakali siyasinda, sihlangulwe kuyo ingqumbo!",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Akukho mntu ujongana naso asimangalele, kungekho bani usibuyekezayo ngezenzo zaso.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Sisiwa emangcwabeni, lilindwe ingcwaba laso.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Amagada entlambo alala athi ncwaba phezu komzimba waso. Bonke abantu bayasilandela ukuya apho; kanti sandulelwe linani elingenakubalwa.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Ningathini ke ukufuna ukundithomalalisa ngamazwi alambathayo? Zonke iingxoxo zenu bubuvuvu obungeyonyaniso.”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku uElifazi umfo waseTeman uphendule wenjenje:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ngaba ukhona na umntu oluncedo kuThixo? Ngaba angazuza lutho na kwinkintsela yesilumko?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Uthi ngaba uSomandla unolutho aluzuzayo ukuba wena ulilungisa? Khona sekusithiwa awunabala, imnceda ntoni loo nto?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Ngaba uThixo angakohlwaya na ngenxa yokuba umthobela, aze akumise enkundleni?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Akungebi ngokuba wone gqitha, nobugwenxa bakho bungenasiphelo?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kaloku wena amawenu uwamisele isibambiso ngaphandle kwesizathu; ude uwohluthe nempahla yawo yokunxiba, asale eze.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Abadiniweyo benxaniwe awuluthobanga unxano lwabo, nabalambileyo ubavimbile ukutya.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Wena ubusisinhanha esinemihlaba; ubungummi obekekileyo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kanti awanelanga kukungancedi bahlolokazi, koko ude waxhaphaza wacinezela neenkedama ezi!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ngoko ke ngoku ubhijelwe zizabatha; uminxwe naliphaphu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngoku ukhulelwe bubumnyama, awuboni; ugutyungelwe naziimpuphuma.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Andithi na kaloku uThixo yena uhlala emajukujukwini amazulu? Neenkwenkwezi ngokwazo kuloo malenga-lenga zikuwo yena uzivelele.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ube ke wena usithi: ‘Wazi ntoni uThixo? Esithwe ziingqimba zamafu nje, angasigweba njani?’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Uthi: ‘Akaboni; uvalelwe ngamafu; kuphela uhamba-hamba phaya esibhakabhakeni.’",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngaba usazimisele ukuhamba indlela yamandulo, ulandele ikhondo labantu abakhohlakeleyo?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kaloku bona baxhwilwe kwangaphambi kwexesha labo; izikhukula zemka neziseko zabo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Aba ngabo babesithi kuThixo: ‘Suka kuthi. Angasenza ntoni na uSomandla?’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kambe ke ikwanguye ozalisa imizi yabo ngobuqhele-qhele. Phofu ke mna andihambisani neqhinga lezikhohlakali.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Amalungisa ayakubona ukutshabalala kwezikhohlakali, asuke avuye; abamsulwa bahlekisa ngazo besithi:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ‘Inene, iintshaba zethu zitshatyalalisiwe, nobutyebi bazo budliwe ngumlilo.’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Ngoko ke wena zilahlele kuThixo, ube noxolo kunye naye; kwakuba njalo ke uya kuzuza okulungileyo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Yamkela imfundiso ephuma emlonyeni wakhe, uwamilisele entliziyweni yakho amazwi akhe.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ewe, ukuba uyabuyela kuSomandla uya kwakheka; nto nje wena lahla la manyondololo aqhubeka kulo mzi wakho.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Igolide yakho yilahle, neyona yodidi yaseOfire yithathe njengamatye nje aphaya entlanjeni.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kuphela igolide yakho mayibe nguSomandla, neengqumba zesiliva yakho mayibe kwanguye.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Wakuba wenjenjalo ke uya kukholosa ngoThixo uSomandla, ubujongise kuye ubuso bakho.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Uya kuthandaza kuye eve; ngokunjalo ke nezibhambathiso zakho uzifezekise.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Izigqibo zakho ziya kuphumelela, ngokunjalo nendlela yakho ibe mhlophe.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Xa abantu bekhahlelwe phantsi uze uthi: ‘Nceda ubaphakamise.’ UThixo uya kubahlangula abazithobileyo;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ewe, ude ahlangule nongekho msulwa, emsindisa ngobunyulu bezandla zakho.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> UYobi uphendule wenjenje:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Nanamhlanje ndisamkhalazela ndikrakra uThixo, kuba undiphethe gadalala nakuba sendincwina kangaka nje!",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Akwaba bendimazi apho akhoyo, ndiyazi nendlela eya apho ahlala khona.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bendiya kusibeka isikhalo sam phambi kwakhe, ndixoxe ndizithethelele.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bendiya kukhe ndimve ukuba uthini na; ndive ukuba uthetha ntoni na.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngaba angasunduzana nam ngaloo mandla akhe? Hayi, uThixo ngeke akwenze oko.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kaloku enkundleni yakhe amalungisa aphuma phambili. Ke ngoko uMgwebi wam ebeya kundigwebela kuphele.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Ndikhangele ndamfuna empumalanga, kodwa andimfumani; ukanti nasentshonalanga andimbhaqanga.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nokuba usebenza kwelasentla andimboni; xa ebuyela kwelasezantsi usithele emehlweni am.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Phofu ke uThixo uyayazi indlela endiyihambayo; ukuba unokukhe andivavanye ndingafumaneka ndimsulwa okwegolide.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kaloku iinyawo zam zilandela emkhondweni wakhe; indlela yakhe ndiyigcinile, andaphambuka kuyo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Andiyishiyanga imiyalelo yemilebe yomlomo wakhe; andenzanga ngokufuna kwam, koko ndiwathobele amazwi akhe.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Xa enze isigqibo ngubani ongamjikayo? Oko afuna ukukwenza uyakwenza.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ngoko ke uya kukufezekisa konke oko andimisele kona, nditsho nokuba yintoni na ayicebileyo ngam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngoko ke ndisuka ndirhwaqele phambi kwakhe; ewe, ndithi ndakucinga ngaye ndinkwantye.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> NguThixo lo unditsho ndoyika kangaka! Ewe, nguSomandla lo undirhwaqelisayo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Phofu bona ubumnyama abundivalanga umlomo, nditsho esi sithokothoko sigqume ubuso bam.”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ngani ukuba uSomandla angalimisi ixesha lokugweba? Kutheni ukuba nâbo bamaziyo bangayiboni loo mini?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Abantu bayawushenxisa umlima-ndlela. Ewe, beba iigusha bazifuye emadlelweni.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bayayohlutha idonki yenkedama; babambisa ngenkabi yenkomo yomhlolokazi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Amahlwempu bayawagila aphume endleleni, babanyanzelisele ekuzimeleni abaziintsizana belizwe.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ewe, abahlelelekileyo bavuka kusasa, bexelengela ukutya kwabo, oku kweqwarha elibhadula ezindle lifuna ukutya koozintlango; yinkqantosi kuphela ebonelela abantwana babo ngokutyiwayo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ukutya kwabo bakuvuna efusini, bakhwahlaze izidiliya zezikhohlakali.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ebusuku balala ngengub' esele; abanazo iingubo zokubakhusela engqeleni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ezintabeni phaya iimvula zibatsho babe manzi tixi, bemana bezikhusela ngokuncathama emaweni.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Abakhohlakeleyo bathimba iintsana eziziinkedama ezisesebeleni; bathatha iintsana zamahlwempu zibe sisibambiso.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ewe, amahlwempu ahamba ze engenampahla; athwala izithungu izisu zithe nca!",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Akhama ioyile eminqumeni, axovule newayini ezidiliyeni; kodwa wona ngokwawo abe enxaniwe.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ezixekweni kuncwina amadoda, iingxwelerha ziyahlahlamba zicela uncedo, kodwa yena uThixo akazisi enkundleni izikhohlakali.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Kukho abantu abangafunaniyo nokukhanya, abangafuni nokuziqonda iindlela zako, futhi bengahambisani nako mpela!",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Izikrelemnqa zivuka ekuseni ziye kugebenga abahlelelekileyo, kuze kuthi kwakuhlwa zijike zibe ngamasela.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ke bona abakrexezi balinda ungcwalazi, ufike sebefihl' ubuso, besithi: ‘Andiyi kubonwa.’",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ebusuku amasela aqhekeza izindlu, aze kwakuba semini azimele angafunani nokukhanya.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Isithoko-thoko sobumnyama sifana nemini kubo; ubusuku oboyikekayo bunjengomhlobo kubo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Isikhohlakali sikhukuliswa sisikhukula; amasimi asisabelo saso ashwatyulelwe, akusekho bani usebenzayo ezidiliyeni zaso.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ikhephu liyanyibilika lakudibana nobushushu nembalela; ngokunjalo naboni bayavuthuluka kwelabafileyo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Nditsho nonina uyamlibala; kaloku umemethwe ziimpethu, akabi sakhunjulwa. Ewe, isikhohlakali sinkumka oku komthi owomileyo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kaloku sona siphanga abafazi abaziindlolo, singabenzeli inceba abahlolokazi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ngamandla akhe uThixo uyazishenxisa izihandiba; ewe, uThixo uthi akusebenzisa amandla akhe zitsho ziphelelwe lithemba lokudla ubomi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> UThixo noba angaziyeka zihlale zithe zava, kodwa usoloko ezijongile ukusuka nokuhlala kwazo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Abantu abakhohlakeleyo bahluma babe nenkqubela okwexeshana, kodwa yonke loo nto iphela ngokukhawuleza; bayadaka bafe njengamntu wonke, bayabuna oku kwesikhwebu sengqolowa esivuniweyo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Ngubani ongayiphikisayo le nyaniso? Makavele ongandiphikisayo, athi nditheth' amampunge!”"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kwesi sithuba ke kuphendule uBhildadi umfo waseShuwa, wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Kaloku uThixo nguSomagunya, nguDuma-barhwaqele; yaye ke ulugcinile ucwangco kweliphezulu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngaba ukhona na ongazibalayo izinxiba-mxhaka zakhe? Khona ngaba kuphi apho lungabonakaliyo ukhanyiso lwakhe?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngaba kungenzeka ukuba umntu afumaniseke emsulwa enkundleni kaThixo? Uthi ingenzeka into yokuba umntu ozelwe ngumfazi angabi nabala?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kaloku nenyanga ngokwayo ayiqaqambanga kangako phambi kwakhe; kanti neenkwenkwezi ezi azingcwenganga kangako kuye.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kuxa engubani ke yena umntu, eyimpethu nje? Uthi unaxabiso lini unyana womntu kuThixo, engumbungu nje?”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke yena uYobi uphendule wenjenje:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Kuthi mandivume ndithi ùluncedo kwababhetye-bhetye! Hayi kambe ukubahlangula kwakho abo baswele amandla!",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ewe, uzicebise kakuhle izityhakala; hayi, ubulumko obubonakalisileyo!",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Phofu uthi ngubani ongade aweve la mazwi akho? Khona futhe lini eli uthetha uphantsi kwalo?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Abafileyo bayabhinyalaza kukunkwantya, kanti ke nelo lamanzi liyazibhija-bhija kunye nabemi balo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ewe, elabafileyo lityhilekile phambi koThixo; ayinasigqubuthelo inzonzobila.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kaloku uThixo wasitwabulula isibhakabhaka ngasentla phaya, waza umhlaba wawujingisa enyanyeni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nguye ofaka amanzi kwiingqimba zamafu, aze loo mafu awabophe angagqajuzwa bobo bunzima bamanzi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Uyayifihla inyanga ingabonakali; ewe, utwabulula ilifu lithi zinzi, itsho ifihlakale.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wakwahlula ukukhanya ebumnyameni ngeso sazinge sizotywe elundini lolwandle.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Uthi angakhalima zitsho zihexe iintsika ezixhase isibhakabhaka; ewe, zitsho zizama-zame zingcangcazele kukoyika.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kaloku yena ngaloo mandla akhe waluthomalalisa ulwandle, waza kwangobo buchule bakhe wamvikiva uRahabhi isilo saselwandle.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngomoya wakhe ufutha sitsho sicwenge isibhakabhaka; kanti ke ikwasisandla sakhe esangxwelerha inyoka enyubelezayo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kambe ke la ngamagqabantshintshi nje amandla akhe. Thina esikuvileyo lumingi-mingi nje! Ibingubani ke ongade akuqonde ukuzongoma kwamandla kaThixo?”"
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku uYobi uphinde wathathisa wenjenje:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ekho nje uThixo, lo undivimb' ubulungisa, nditsho uSomandla lo uwenze umphefumlo wam wangcamla ubukrakra:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ukuba ndisaxomoloza ndisadl' amazimba, xa ngaba ndisaphila ndinomphefumlo kaThixo emathatheni am,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> imilebe yam ayisokuze ithethe inkohlakalo, ngokunjalo nolwimi lwam alusoze luthethe inkohliso.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Andisoze ndithi ninyanisile, futhi ndiya kude ndife ndibambelele kwinyaniso yokuba ndimsulwa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ndiya kuthi nca kwinto yokuba ndililungisa; andisoze ndibe nasazela yonke imihla yam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Akwaba utshaba lwam lwafumana isohlwayo sabakhohlakeleyo, ngokunjalo nombandezeli wam azuze isiphelo sabangenabulungisa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Liyintoni na ithemba labangenaThixo mhla wabunqumla ubomi babo uThixo?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Xa sele kunyembelekile kubo, uthi uThixo angaze asive isikhalo sabo?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Khona bangaziyolisa na ngoSomandla? Bangamnqula na uThixo ngamaxesha onke?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Makhe ndinifundise ngobukhulu bamandla kaThixo; mandingazifihli izicwangciso zikaSomandla.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hayi gxebe, senizibonele nje ngokwenu; ngani ke ukuba nibe sathetha imfungu-mfungu enje?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Naso ke isabelo sezikhohlakali kuThixo; elo ke lilifa lezibhoja kuSomandla.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Noba zingade zibe nenyambalala yoonyana bosuka babe lilifa lekrele emfazweni; ewe, inzala yazo yasoloko ithiwe nca liphango!",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nemingqandanda esindileyo itshayelwa ngubhubhani, baze nabahlolokazi bazo bangalili nokulila.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Noba zingade zibe nemfumba yesiliva ngathi luthuli, zibe nempahla yokwambatha efumbe okodongwe,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> kosuka kuthi gqi lungisa lithile inxitywe lilo loo mpahla; kosuka kuvele abantu abamsulwa babelane ngaloo siliva.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Isikhohlakali sakha indlu efana nesingxobo seqonya; sakha into engathi liphempe labalindi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Isikhohlakali silala sinobutyebi, kodwa siyagqibelisa – sivuka sebuphel' emehlweni.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sisuka sirhwaqele ngathi siyarhaxwa; kaloku sitshayelwa sisaqhwithi ngobhadakazi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kufika umoya wasempuma usitshayele, usuke usinqukrule singabi sazana nekhaya laso.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Usuka usilenge ungenalusini tu; nakanjani kufuneka siwasabe amandla awo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ewe, umoya usiqhwabela izandla, usihewule isikhohlakali simke endaweni yaso.”"
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ewe, ikho imigodi yesiliva; ngokunjalo zikho neendawo zokuhluza igolide.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Abantu bemba isinyithi emhlabeni, baze banyibilikise ubhedu olusematyeni.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Nenzonzobila yobumnyama abantu bayayihlola-hlola; baphicotha namathumbu omhlaba, baze bembe bacubungule kwimiwewe enzongo-nzongo yenzonzobila.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kude lé kwelimiweyo, apho kungazange kwathi cakatha mntu, abantu bayemba bavule imigodi, bajinga-jinge kwalunkcwe, bebotshelelwe ngeentambo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Phezulu apha lo mhlaba uvelisa ukudla; kanti ngaphantsi phaya ubhukuqwa ngathi ngumlilo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumatye omhlaba kuphuma iisafire, kanti ke lona uthuli lwawo luvelisa igolide.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Amaxhalanga ngokwawo akazazi iindlela zasemigodini phaya, ngokunjalo zange zalanywa naliliso likakhetshe.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Amarhamncwa anyalasayo akazange athi cakatha unyawo apho, nkqu nengonyama ayizange yadlula khona.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kaloku abantu baqhekeza bagqale nditsho nenyengane le; ewe, neentaba ngokwazo bayazibhukuqa, bazisiphule neengcambu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Basuka bagqobhoze iitonela emaweni, lize iliso labo liwabhaqe amatye axabisekileyo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Imithombo yakhona bayayivingca ingampompozi, baze bazidandalazise izinto ezifihlakeleyo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Kambe ke, bungaze bufumaneke phi ubulumko? Khona lona ulwazi lungazuzwa phi?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ewe, ubulumko abunakufumaneka ebantwini; kaloku akukho namnye ulaziyo nexabiso labo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Andithi na kaloku kwankqu neenzonzobila ezinzongo-nzongo, nditsho neelwandle, ziyabulandula?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kaloku bona abungekhe bufumaneke nangegolide ecikizekileyo, kanti nentabalala yesiliva ayinako ukubuhlawula.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Neyona golide yaseOfire iyalaba-laba kwixabiso labo; nditsho namatye exabiso, nokuba yionike okanye yisafire.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ewe, abunakulinganiswa negolide, ukanti abunakuthelekiswa nayo nemveliso yegolide, nditsho nayo neglasi yodidi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Asisathethi ke ngeekorale neekristale, kuba kaloku bona ubulumko bubalasele ngexabiso, ndithi bugqwesa kwaiiperile.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ewe, netopazi yaseKushe ayinakulinganiswa nabo, ngokunjalo abunakuthengwa nangeyona ihluziweyo igolide.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ke, ngaba uphi owona mthombo wobulumko? Umntu angalufumana phi ulwazi?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Abubonakali kuzo zonke izinto eziphilileyo, nditsho nakweyona intingayo intaka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ewe, nokufa nentshabalalo, zombini ziyavuma, zithi: ‘Luvakele nje umingi-mingi ngabo ezindlebeni zethu!’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> NguThixo kuphela owaziyo ngobulumko; nguye owaziyo umthombo wabo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kaloku yena ubona nditsho namaphethelo ehlabathi, kuba kuye akukho nanye into efihlakeleyo phantsi kwamazulu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ngokuya uThixo wayemisela umoya amandla awo, namanzi ewacandela umda wawo,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> nemvula eyenzela ummiselo wayo, nombane ewalathisa indlela,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> kanye ngelo thuba ke uThixo wabubona wabuphicotha ubulumko, waza ke wabumisela wabugoca-goca.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ke uluntu waluyalela wathi: ‘Niyabona, ofuna ubulumko makathobele uThixo; ofuna ukuzuza ulwazi makabucezele ububi.’ ”"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku uYobi wathathisa wathetha wenjenje:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Awu, akwaba ibinokubuyiselwa kum imihla yamandulo, ngokuya uThixo wayesandilondolozile,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> xenikweni isibane sakhe besikhanya phezu kwentloko yam, xa ndanditabhata nasebumnyameni endikhanyisela.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ewe, ngaloo mihla yamfamlibe ndandimi kakuhle; bendilala ngangubo-nye noThixo emzini wam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> USomandla wayengakum ngoko, ndiphahlwe ngabantwana bam.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngaloo mihla amasi ayedlal' abantwana kwam; ke yona iminquma ichuma nasematyeni, ithulula ioyile.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Ndandisithi ndakufika enkundleni ngasesangweni, ndakuthi zinzi phakathi kwamadoda amakhulu,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> abafana bathi gu bucala, ke zona iingwevu zime ngeenyawo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ewe, ayesuka aphel' emqaleni kumatshawe, ufike selethe khebevu!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Izikhulu zazisithi cwaka ngathi ulwimi lukhulekiwe enkalakahleni.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Abandiva ndithetha babendincoma, kanti ababona izinto endizenzayo babendingqinela.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kaloku ndandisabela ndiwahlangule amahlwempu esakukhala; ukanti ndazibonelela neenkedama ezazingenamncedi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ababesindakala ndaza ndabanceda babendincoma, ukanti nabahlolokazi ndandibanceda batsho baba neengoma ezintliziyweni zabo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ndandivatha ubulungisa njengesinxibo sam; ukwenza okulungileyo kwakuyingubo yam neqhiya yam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ndandingamehlo kwiimfama, ndiziinyawo koqhwalelayo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ndandingutata kumahlwempu, neengxaki zabasemzini bendizithabathela kum.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Yayindim umaphul' iimpondo kwizibhoja, amaxhoba azo ndiwathi hlasi emilonyeni yazo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Ndandisithi: ‘Ndiya kukhula ndide ndikhokhobe endlwini yam, nemihla yam ibe mininzi njengentlabathi.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ndandifana nomthi ongcambu zinabele emanzini, omasebe asoloko elalelwa ngumbethe.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Udumo lwam lwaluhlala luhlaziyeka, amandla am engapheli nokuphela.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Ndandisithi ndakuthetha kutsho kuthi cwaka, abantu bewaphulaphula amacebiso am.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ndandilebela xa ndithethayo, kungekho mntu unokongeza; kaloku amazwi am ayezika njengemvula.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ndandilangazelelwa oku kwemvula, amazwi am bewaginya oku komhlaba uginy' imvula entlakohlaza.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Babekhuthazeka ndakuncuma; ukukhululeka kobuso bam bekubomeleza.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ndandingqendeva njengomnumzana, ndithethe kume ngam; ndandibakhokela njengenjengele kwimikhosi yayo; ndandibaxhasa njengothuthuzela abadakumbileyo.”"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Xa kunamhlanje-nje sendisisigculelo nakubafana abayise bendingabazele nto, ebendingeze ndabashiya nezinja zam ezalusa iigusha.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bebeligquba nje ekungekho yalo, amabhetye-bhetye angenakwenza nto tu!",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bangamahlwempu alambayo, ahamba ngobusuku, ufike enqunquda iingcambu emqwebedwini phaya.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Balamba kangangokuba ungafika besimba iinqoba emqwebedwini, bade batye neengcambu zemithi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Abantu babagxothile phakathi kwabo; basuke babahewula bangathi bachil' isela!",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kuye kwanyanzeleka ukuba baye kuhlala emiqolombeni, emingxunyeni, nasezimfanteni emaweni.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bakhonya phakathi kwamatyholo, ufike sebethe buthalala phantsi kwemithi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Awu, ziinjubaqa; sisizukulwana soongantweni eside sagxothwa nakwelakowazo!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Ngoku ke sebendicabela nasezingomeni zabo; ewe, sendisisimbo nesigculelo sabo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ewe, ngoku bandidelile, bayandenyanya; bathi bangandibona banditshicele ebusweni!",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngenxa yokuba uThixo undiyekele ndatsho ndangugqush' eluthulini, nabo ke ngoku baziqhawule iintambo zokulawulwa ndim.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngasekunene bafunzela ukundihlasela belihlokondiba; ewe, bayandijoka, futhi sebezimisele ukundihlabanisela.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bayandiqhiwulela endleleni, befuna ukundigqiba, besithi: ‘Akanabani ongamncedayo.’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bandihlasela ngathi batyhoboza kwindawo ebanzi; baphoseka kum becanda amabhodlo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngoku ke sendirhawulwe kukunkwantya; isidima sam sivuthuluke ngathi siyavuthelwa, ukukhuseleka kwam kubhange oku komfankungu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Ngoku ndisebugxwayibeni, kuba imihla yenkathazo indibambile.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ebusuku ndiqaqanjelwa nangamathambo la; iintlungu ezindidlayo azipheli.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ndigxavulwa ngeempahla zokunxiba, ndidlakazeliswe; ndiyakrwitshwa sisambatho, ndibanjwe ngobhongwana.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> UThixo undiphose eludakeni; andisento, sendifana nothuli nothuthu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ndiba ngakhala ndikubongoza, akundiphenduli; ndiba ngazibika kuwe, akundihoyi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Wena ngoku ujike wandikhohlakalela, undihlasela ngengalo yakho enamandla.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Uyandiphakamisa undiyekele ngomoya undibhudle; ndiyaqotha-qotheka ndiqwengwa sisaqhwithi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ndiyaqonda ke ukuba undinikezela ekufeni, apho baya kuphelela khona bonke abaphilayo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Kambe akukho hlwempu elizibikayo endingalincedanga, nditsho elaliphakamisela izandla kum licela uncedo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Andithi na kaloku ndandilila kunye nabasezingxakini, umphefumlo wam udandatheka ngenxa yamahlwempu?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Mna ndithe ndijonge okuhle kwathi gqi okubi; bendilindele ukukhanya, suka kwathi nyalulu ubumnyama.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ndithiwe fithi lunxunguphalo, alundiphe thuba; imihla ngemihla ndihlangatyezwa yinkathazo.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ukukhanya akukho, ndihamba ndigutyungelwe bubumnyama; into endiyenzayo embizweni kukuzibika.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ngoku sendingumlingane woodyakalashe; ewe, ndiliqabane leenciniba.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ulusu lwam selujike lwamnyama, futhi luyaxobuka, ibe ke nomzimba wam lo uyagcadeka.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ihapu yam ngoku seyijike yaba yeyesililo, nefluthi yam ngoku seyisenza isijwili.”"
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ke mna ke sendazimisela ngomxhelo wam wonke ukuba kungáze kubekho ntombi ndiyincwasayo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ke, siyintoni isabelo somntu kuThixo? Liyintoni ilifa kuSomandla kweliphezulu?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Abangalunganga ubathwaxa ngezibetho, aze abo bangamatshijolo abayekele ngentlekele.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Andithi na kaloku yena uyazazi iindlela zam, ewabala onke amanyathelo am?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Ndiqinisekile andizange ndenze buqhophololo, ndingazanga ndakhohlisa mntu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Makhe ndibekwe esikalini kungekho xanasi ukuze uThixo aqonde ukuba ndimsulwa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ukuba ngaba nditenxile endleleni, ndaza ke ndabhaduliswa yiminqweno, okanye ukuba izandla zam zidyojwe bububi,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> izilimo zam mazixhatshazwe mntu wumbi, yonke into endiyilimileyo mayincothulwe neengcambu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Ukuba ngaba ndikhe ndancwasa omnye umfazi, okanye ndaya kumxhwarhela ngasemasangweni ommelwane,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> umfazi wam ngamana wagubela enye indoda; ewe, ngamana wambathwa bantu bambi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kuba eso ingaba sisenzo esigwenxa, ingaba lityala elifanelwe kukugwetywa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Loo nto ingaba njengomlilo otshabalalisayo, otshisa yonke imveliso yam.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Ukuba ndakha ndasigatya isikhalazo sesicaka sam, okanye andasihoya isicakazana xa sinesikrokro ngakum,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bendingathini ke ukujongana noThixo? Ndingathini ukuphendula xa efuna ingxelo?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Andithi na kaloku kwalo Thixo udale mna zikwadalwe nguye nezicaka zam!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Mna andizange ndikumangale ukunceda amahlwempu, nabahlolokazi abazange bemke belambatha kum.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Andizange ndaneliseke kukutya ndedwa, ibe yona inkedama ingenayo into etyiwayo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kaloku ndayikhulisa njengoyise kwasebuntwaneni bayo, ndayondla ndayithantamisa kwasekuzalweni kwayo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ndakubona usizana oluze, oluhlwempuzeke kangangokuba lungabi nayo impahla yokunxiba,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bendilunika impahla eyenziwe ngoboya obuyimveliso yeegusha zam, lutsho lundincome luhambe lundidumisa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngaba ndakha ndayivuyelela inkedama kuba ndiqhayisa ngokuyitshonisa nasenkundleni?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Xa kunjalo ke ngamana ndakroboka iingalo; akwaba zingancothuka emagxeni am.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hayi bo! Ngenxa yokoyika isohlwayo sikaThixo, nangenxa yokuhlonipha ubuhandiba bakhe, into enjalo andizange ndayenza.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Xa bendingaqamelela ngegolide, kwecikizekileyo ndisithi: ‘Ulithemba lam!’",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ukuba bendivuye ndada ndaqholosa ngenxa yentabalala yobutyebi bam, nangenxa yokwanda kwemveliso yam,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> ukuba bendisuke ndanqula ilanga ngenxa yokuqaqamba kwalo, okanye inyanga ngenxa yomfaneleko wayo,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ukuba ngaba bendiwexulekile ndasanga isandla sam, ndibusa zona ezi zinto,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> nale ke into ibingaba bubugwenxa obufanele isohlwayo esiqatha, kuba ukwenjenjalo ingaba kukuvukelana noThixo kweliphezulu.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Andizange ndavuyiswa kukubandezeleka kotshaba lwam, ndingazange ndakuthakazelela ukuminxeka kwalo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Andizange umlomo wam ndiwuvule wone ngokusuka ndilushwabulele utshaba lwam.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Namadoda andisebenzelayo akazange athi: ‘Yhu, besilamba phaya kwaYobi!’",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Abahambi abazange balale ecaleni lendlela ndikho; ndiyabamema beze, kuba iingcango zomzi wam zahlala zivulekile.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bambi bayazigusha bazifihle iziphoso zabo, kambe ke mna andibufihli ubugwenxa bam.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kuba mna andiboyiki abantu, andithi cwaka okanye ndizivalele endlwini, kuba ndisoyika ukunyenjwa zizalamane.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Akwaba bekukho ondiphulaphuleyo! Ndiwandlalile umcimbi wam; uSomandla makandiphendule. Akwaba izityholo endibekwa zona ngondimangalelayo bezibhaliwe.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bendiya kuzithwala emagxeni, ndizithi jize ngazo entloko njengentshinga.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> UThixo bendiya kumanekela konke okwam, ndingqiyaze phambi kwakhe njengetshawe.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> “Ukuba ngaba umhlaba wam ubundenzela isijwili, zindigxeka neefolo zawo,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> ukuba nditye imveliso yawo ndingabahlawulanga abaniniwo, ndaza bona abalimi bawo ndabavimba,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> ewe, endaweni yengqolowa mawuvelise imithi enameva, ukuze endaweni yerhasi uvelise ukhula.” Waba njalo ke uyaphetha uYobi: ncincilili-i-i!"
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku la madoda mathathu ade amncama uYobi, kuba yena wasuka wanje, esithi umsulwa yena.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ke yena uElihu unyana kaBharakeli wendlu kaRam eBhuzi uthe akuyiqonda le meko wasuka wakhathazeka, kuba kaloku uYobi wayezenza ilungisa esola uThixo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Futhi wakhathazwa nayinto yokuba ezi zihlobo zikaYobi zithathu zisuke zoyiswa kukuphendulana noYobi, zingabanga nako ukudandalazisa ubutyala bakhe, kodwa zimtyhola.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> UElihu lo wayesalindele ukuthetha noYobi, kuba abanye aba babebadala kunaye.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Athe ke la madoda mathathu akuba selethethe koma umqala esoyiswa bubuciko bukaYobi, wakhathazeka,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> wangenelela ke yena uElihu unyana kaBharakeli waseBhuzi, wathi: “Kambe ke ndiyimveku ngeminyaka, ke nina senikhulile, niziingwevu, nto leyo ke esuke yanditsho ndamathidala, ndoyika ukuphuhlisa olwam uluvo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ndithe: ‘Mandiyekel' iminyak' isiphakele.’ Bendisithi: ‘Izilimela zingasiph' ubulumko.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kambe ke ngoku ndiyaqonda ukuba ngumoya osemntwini, ewe, lifuthe likaSomandla elimthi jize ngokuqonda umntu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hayi, abuyi ngaminyaka ubulumko, kungayi nangabudala ukuqonda imfanelo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Ngoko ke bekan' iindlebe, khe ndiniphakele; makhe ndinivakalisel' olwam uluvo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ewe, ndiniphulaphule xa beniphakula ubulumko benu; ndibuvisisile xa benidimbaza nigalela.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bendiziindlebe ndonke xa benithetha; akukho namnye umchaniley' uYobi, kungekho namnye ukwaziy' ukuchan' amagama.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ke nina sanukuthi: ‘Sibuzuzile ubulumko.’ Kaloku nguThixo yedwa ongaphendulanayo noYobi, hayi umntu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> UYobi ubebhekisa kuni, ingekum. Kambe ke bendingamphenduli njengani mna.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Hayi, Yobi, bathethe kom' umqala; kungokunje basik' umlomo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Mandithini na ke mna? Uthi mandithi cwaka kuba nabo bethule? Ewe, nâbo bethe bhuxe, inkukw' isik' umlomo!",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hayi bo! Nam makhe ndenze owam umda, ndiluvakalise nolwam uluvo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hayi, mna andisenakuzibamba ndithi cwaka, kuba kuninzi ukuthetha kum.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hayi, ngenene ndifana nemvaba yewayini ebila ingavulwanga – xa ndingaphokozi ndosuka ndigqabhuke.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ewe, manditheth' ukuze kuthi qabu; mandiwuvule umlomo wam ndiphendule.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Mna andiz' ukuceng' usolala phi, ndiza kutheth' utyhatyhiwe ndingalalanisi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kambe akunto yam ukulalanisa; xa bekunjalo uMdali wam ebengandicim' igama ngoko nangoko!"
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ewe ke ngoku, Yobi, khawukuve ukuthetha kwam, uwaphulaphule onke amazwi am.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Khawundibolek' iindlebe, nam khe ndikuphokozele. Phulaphula, ulwimi lwam selubeth' inkalakahla.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ewe kaloku, ndithetha ndinyanisekile; andikufihli oko ndikwaziyo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kaloku nam ndidalwe nguMoya kaThixo; ukuphefumla kukaSomandla kundidlise ubomi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ndiphendule ukuba unako; qula uzilungiselele amagama.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kaloku phambi koThixo siyafana sobabini; ewe, sobabini sabunjwa nguye ngodongwe.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngoko ke uzungatatazeli, mwethu; noko nesandla sam asingeke sikucinezele.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Ngokuya ubuthetha ndikuvisisile; kaloku uthethe wenjenje:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ‘Mna ndimsulwa, andinatyala; andinachaphaza, ndingenasiphoso.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Koko uThixo uyandidlelelela nje; ewe, ufumana endityhola ngokuba ndilutshaba!",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Iinyawo zam uzikhonkxa ngezikhuni; uyazigqala zonke iindlela zam.’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Uyabona, uphazamile ngayo le ndawo; mandikuphendule, kuba uThixo yena mkhulu kunomntu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngani ke ukuba umangalelane naye, usithi yena akaphenduli mntu?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Kaloku uThixo uthetha nomntu ngandlela zonke, kambe ke yena umntu akahoyi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Xa umntu ekobunzulu ubuthongo, elele emandlalweni wakhe, uThixo uthetha ngamaphupha nemibono yasebusuku.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ewe, uzivula ngelo xesha iindlebe zabantu, ebalumkisa batsho barhwaqele.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ethethanje ke uthintela ukona; unqanda umntu angazigwagwisi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ukhusela umphefumlo womntu engcwabeni, amhlangule kwintshabalalo yekrele.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Kananjalo umntu wolulekwa nangezigulo ezibuhlungu, aphanjwe ziingqaqambo emzimbeni.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ewe, ude angabi sakulangazelela nokutya, nokona kumnandi akucekise.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ubhitya abe ngumcinga, nezo mbanjana zakhe bezifihlakele zithi gqi ngaphandle.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kaloku selejinga phezu kwengcwaba; ubomi bakhe bukhwetywa kukufa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Mhlawumbi ke angeza kulamlelwa sisithunywa, esinye kuloo mawaka-waka, simkhumbuze ngeemfanelo zakhe.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Singatsho ngovelwano sithi: ‘Mkhulule; makangehli aye kwelabafileyo. Nantsi kaloku intlawulo.’",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ulusu lwakhe luya kuhlaziyeka njengolosana, lubuyiselwe kwimihla yobutsha bakhe;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> athi ke akuthandaza eviwe nguThixo, atsho amnqule ngothakazelelo, abuye abe ngumntu oziphethe ngaloo ndlela ayifunayo uThixo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Uya kuvuma esidlangalaleni athi: ‘Ndonile ndaphambuka endleleni, kodwa uThixo akandohlwayanga ngako oko bekundifanele.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ewe, undihlangule engcwabeni, nobomi bam abuyi kucinyelwa langa.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Zonke ezi zinto ke zenziwa nguThixo; ewe, uzenza umhla nezolo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Umntu uyamhlangula engcwabeni, ukuze naye axhamle ubomi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Ngamana wandiphulaphula ke, Yobi; ewe, yithi cwaka khe ndithethe.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kambe ke uphendule xa unako; nam ndizimisele ukukulungiselela.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Phofu ke, xa ungenamazwi, yithi tu, mna ndikufundise ubulumko.”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke uElihu utyatyadule wenjenje:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Hoyina, nani nina zilumko; khanibek' iindlebe, nani zingqondi!",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ukutya kungcanyulwa lulwimi, ke yona intetho iviwa ziindlebe.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Makhe sikhethe oko kulungileyo; ewe, masiphicothe oko kufanelekileyo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Kaloku uYobi uthi: ‘Ndimsulwa, kodwa uThixo undivimb' ubulungisa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nangona ndinyanisekile, ndiphathwa okwexoki; nangona ndingenatyala, utolo lwakhe lundingxwelerhile.’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Wakha wakho phi ofana noYobi lo, osoloko ehlalele ukuphoxisa,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> umnt' osoloko ethene mbende nabenzi bobubi, ohlal' eqhogene nezikhohlakali?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kaloku yena uthi: ‘Akumncedi lutho umntu ukuzimisela ukukholisa uThixo.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Kambe ke ndiphulaphuleni, zingqondi: kukude lé kuThixo ukwenza ububi, kuSomandla ukwenza ubugwenxa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kuye umntu uvuna loo nto ayilimileyo; umntu umphatha ngokwehambo yakhe.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hayi bo, uThixo akayenzi inkohlakalo; uSomandla akabugqwethi ubulungisa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kakade ngubani owammiselayo ukuba alawule ihlabathi? Ngubani owambeka ukuba alongamele lonke elimiweyo?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Xa ebenokusuka azimisele awunqamle umoya wakhe nempefumlelo yakhe",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> konke okuphilayo kungasuka kutshabalale, noluntu lonke lubuyele kwaseluthulini.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Ngaba uyaqiqa na – phulaphula ke! Bek' iindlebe ndithethe.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Umchasi-mthetho angalawula njani? Ke wena ungamgweba njani uThixo eyingangalala yelungisa nje?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kaloku nakukumkani yena unokuthi: ‘Awunto yanto;’ aze kwizidwangube athi: ‘Nizizinto ezikhohlakeleyo.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> UThixo akakhethi buso nakumatshawe; nesityebi akasilungiseleli ngaphezu kwehlwempu; kaloku bonke bangumsebenzi wezandla zakhe.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bafa ngephanyazo ezinzulwini zobusuku; bayagungqiswa abantu, bafe; kwanezihandiba ziyawa zingawiswanga mntu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Kaloku yena uzijongile iindlela zabantu; uwabona onke amanyathelo abo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kaloku akukho thunzi nantsunguzi yabumnyama apho abenzi bobubi bangazifihla khona.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> KuThixo akuyomfuneko ukubancwina ngakumbi abantu xenikweni ebasa ematyaleni.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> KuThixo akukho mfuneko yaluphando xa abakhiqayo abasezintanjeni, aze amisele abanye ezikhundleni zabo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kaloku uyazazi izenzo zabo; ubabhukuqa ngobusuku babhange.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Xa sukuba ebohlwaya ngenxa yobugwenxa babo, loo nto uyenza esidlangalaleni.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Andithi na kaloku basuke bakreqa, ababi sazikhathalela iindlela zakhe?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ohlelelekileyo bamtsho wazibika kuThixo, waza ke yena wasiva isikhalo sabasweleyo.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Xa athe cwaka ngubani ongamgwebayo? Naxa efihle ubuso bakhe ngubani ongambonayo? Nguye ngokwakhe olawula uluntu nezizwe,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ukuze athintele isikhohlakali ekulawuleni, singababekeli umgibe abantu.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Ukuba ngaba umntu ebenokuthi kuThixo: ‘Ndikuvukele, kodwa andiyi kuphinda ndone.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ndifundise oko ndingenako ukukubona. Ukuba ndenze ubugwenxa andisayi kuphinda ndenjenjalo.’",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ngaba uThixo uthi useza kumohlwaya ngenxa yokumvukela kwakhe? Zikhethele ngokwakho, ingabi ndim. Into oyaziyo yithethe.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Kambe ke iingqondi zosuka zithi, ewe, izilumko zona zingathi:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> ‘UYobi uthethiswa kukungazi; ewe, akathethi, koko uyabhibhidla.’",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Akwaba uYobi ebenokucikidwa ngokupheleleyo, kuba impendulo yakhe ifana neyendoda ekhohlakeleyo.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ewe, esi sono sakhe uyasandisa, kuba kaloku usuka adlongozele, aqhwabe ngolunya izandla zakhe phakathi kwethu, atheth' umlembelele ngoThixo.”"
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> UElihu uqhube wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ucinga ukuba bubulungisa na obu? Kaloku uthi: ‘Ndiya kugwetyelwa nguThixo.’",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kanti ubhekisa kuThixo usithi: ‘Khon' ukuba ndonile ke? Kundinceda ngani ukungoni?’",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Ke ngoku mna ndiza kukuphendula, wena ngokunjalo nabahlobo bakho.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Khawuqethuke ujonge amazulu, uwabone la mafu aphezu kwakho.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Noba uyona awumchukumisi nganto uThixo; ewe, awumenzi nto noba ungade uphinda-phinde!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ukulungisa kwakho kumnceda ngantoni ke? Ewe, uThixo akazuzi nto esandleni sakho.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ukona kwakho kuphazamisa kwa-abantu, nokulungisa kwakho kunceda kwabona.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Abantu bayakhala ngenxa yobuninzi bengcinezelo; balangazelela ukukhululeka kwisandla sabanamandla.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kodwa yinqaba ukubhenela kuThixo uMdali wabo ozisa ithemba xa sukuba lixubayele.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nguye osinika ulwazi kunezilwanyana; yena usenza silumke kuneentaka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Abantu noba sebekhala, uThixo akaphenduli, kuba abakhohlakeleyo bathiwe lwale likratshi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Inene, uThixo akangeke awaphulaphule amampunge; uSomandla akawasi so tu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kunjalo maxa usithi akumboni uThixo, usithi umcimbi wakho uphambi kwakhe, usithi ulinde yena,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> naxa uthi uThixo akacaphuki ohlwaye, usithi akasihoyi isono.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ke uYobi uthetha amampunge, wenza umlembelele engenalwazi.”"
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> UElihu uqhube wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Kambe ke khawundinyamezele kancinci, kuba kusekho ekufuneka ndikuthethe ndimele uThixo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Olwam ulwazi luvela kude; lucacisa ukuba uThixo, uMdali wam, lilungisa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kaloku akukho buxoki kula mazwi am – ophakathi kwenu unolwazi olugqibeleleyo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> UThixo womelele, kodwa akadeleli mntu; unamandla, nolwazi lwakhe alugungqi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Izikhohlakali akaziyeki zidle ubomi, kodwa uyabazelelela abo bahlelelekileyo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Akawasusi amehlo akhe kumalungisa. Nguye obeka ookumkani ezihlalweni, abanye abayeke apho ixesha elide. Kodwa ukuba bayaziphakamisa",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bakhonkxwa ngamatyathanga, bebanjiwe ngezintya zeentlupheko.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> UThixo ubatyhilela izenzo zabo, esalatha izikreqo zabo xa babeziphakamisa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kaloku yena ubenza balulamele ululeko; ubayalela ukuba bahlukane nobugwenxa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ukuba ke bayamva bemthobela uThixo, boyigqiba imihla yabo bexhamla indyebo, neminyaka yabo ibe yeyokwaneliseka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kambe ke xa bengeva baya kutshabalala ngekrele, bafe ngenxa yokuswela kwabo ulwazi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Abantliziyo zingenaThixo bazongezelela ingqumbo yakhe; abazibiki kuye naxa bekhonkxiwe.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bona bafa besebatsha, bexhwalekile ngamahlazo abahlala kuwo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kambe uThixo uyabafundisa abantu nangehambo-nzima; ubavula iindlebe ngokusebenzisa nembandezelo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Nawe wakukhupha enkathazweni, wakutsho waxhamla intlala-kahle, usitya uhlutha, ungaswele nto.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kodwa ngoku isohlwayo esifanele abakhohlakeleyo siphezu kwakho; ukugwetywa nokohlwaywa kukufikele.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Lumka ke umsindo wakho ungawenzi umgibe wokubambisa abanye, ungazimiseli ukusebenzisa ukunyoba okukhulu ukuguqula imeko.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ngaba kukubhomboloza kwakho na okunokukunceda? Hayi bo, yonke imigudu yakho ayingeke incede.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sukulangazelela ukuza kobusuku, xesha elo batshabalala ngalo abantu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Lumka ungayi ebubini; ungazilahleli kubo ngenxa yokubandezeleka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kaloku uThixo yimbalasane ngamandla; ke kumba wokufundisa uyingcungela.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> UThixo akaxelelwa mntu amakakwenze; ngubani onokuthi kuye: ‘Wenze okugwenxa’?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Khumbula uwuphakamise umsebenzi wakhe, lowo abantu bawubongayo ngeengoma.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bonke abantu bayayibona imisebenzi yakhe, noxa beyibona bekude nje.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hayi ukuba mkhulu kukaThixo! Uyiphakamele ingqiqo yethu; inani leminyaka yakhe aligocagoceki.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Nguye ofunxa amanzi emhlabeni, awajike awenze amathontsi emvula,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> mvula leyo ina iphuma emafini, ibe zizandyondyo kumntu wonke.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ngubani okuqondayo ukuhamba kwamafu, nokuzongoma kweendudumo ezulwini phaya?",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Yena utshawuzisa umbane esibhakabhakeni; nguye ogubungela inzonzobila yolwandle.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Le yindlela aluxhasa ngayo uluntu, aluthi jize ngendyikityha yendyebo.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ke yona imibane iselulawulweni lwesandla sakhe; uyayiyalela itsho ichan' ucwethe.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kambe ke sona isiphango sixelwa ziindudumo, nditsho neenkomo ziyakwazi ukuza kwaso."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Kuthi ke kwakuba njalo isuke igubhe intliziyo yam, ixhume endaweni yayo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Khanikuve ukuzongoma kwelizwi lakhe, niphulaphule ukungqokola okuphuma emlonyeni wakhe.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Utshawuzisa imibane esibhakabhakeni, ayithumele eziphelweni zehlabathi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ikhatshwa kukududuma kwelizwi lakhe, lizongoma ngezwi lobungangamsha bakhe. Xa avakalisa izwi lakhe kuba zizabhokhwe zombane ezingathintelekiyo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ewe, uThixo wenza imimangaliso ngezwi lakhe, utsho ngezinto ezinkulu esingenako ukuziqonda.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Uthi kwikhephu: ‘Yiwa emhlabeni;’ kwimikhwitsho yemvula athi: ‘Yenza izandyondyo zomvimbi.’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ke bona abantu batsho bayeke ukusebenza; kaloku ngoku nguye osebenzayo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Iinyamakazi zitsho zingene emingxunyeni yazo, zizimele apho ezikhundleni zazo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Iinkqwithela ziphuma endaweni yazo, imimoya enamandla ize nengqele.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> UThixo uthi angaphefumla amanzi atsho abe ngumkhenkce, ububanzi bawo buqine bukhenkcezeke.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kanti wona amafu uwahlohl' ukufuma, aze awahlwayele imibane.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kaloku nguThixo owalawulayo, atsho enze eyakhe imiyalelo kulo lonke elimiweyo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Unethisa imvula emhlabeni; kanti isenokuba sisibetho ebantwini, kwanjengokuba isenokuba ngumqondiso wothando lwakhe.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Yobi, khawunqumame wondele, ujonge imimangaliso kaThixo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Uyakwazi ukuhamba komyalelo kaThixo, esithi umbane mawulenyeze emafini?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Amafu la uthi ajinga kanjani esibhaka-bhakeni, into emangalisayo engumsebenzi walowo unolwazi olugqibeleleyo?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Uxakwa nje kukuzikhusela ngezambatho kwifuthe lolophu,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ungathini ukufuna ukubambisana naye xa atwabulula isibhakabhaka, esenza somelele okwesipili esityhidiweyo?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Khawutsho, uthi masithini ke kuThixo? Kaloku kumnyama kuthi; asinamhlaba wakuziphendulela!",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Uthi masicele ukuthetha naye! Ngubani ongazibizela intshabalalo?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bekungekho bani unako ukubona ukukhanya; ukuqaqamba kwako bekusithwe ngamafu, kodwa kwakudlula umoya, kuthi qwenge.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Emantla phaya ukukhanya busabugoliderha; isihomo sikaThixo sisitsho sinkwantye ke thina.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Amandla akhe amtsho angafikeleleki; usulungekile, ebalasele ngobulungisa; akukho bani amcinezelayo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngenxa yaloo nto ke, abantu bayamhlonela; kambe ke zona izindwebi akazikhathalele.”"
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke *uNdikhoyo waphendula esesaqhwithini, wathetha noYobi wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Wena kuxa ungubani, ukuba ude ufune ukulenza mfiliba icebo lam? Mazwi mani wona la, engenalwazi nje?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Khawuqule, ume njengendoda; mna ndiza kukubuza, wena ke uphendule.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Wawuphi xa ndiseka ihlabathi? Yitsho kaloku, uyingqondi andithi?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngubani owamisa ubungakanani balo? Awunakungayazi loo nto! Ngubani owalijikelezayo etsala intambo?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Khona, zixhaswe yintoni iintsika zalo? Ingubani owalimisela ilitye lesiseko?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngaloo ntsasa iinkwenkwezi zamemelela, izidwangube zakwaThixo zona zanemincili.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Mhla lwagqabhuka ulwandle emhlabeni, ngubani owalumisela imida?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kaloku ndim owalwambathisa ngamafu, ndaza ndalusonga ngobumnyama.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ndim owalumisela imida, ndalubiyela ndaluvalela endaweni yalo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ndaluyalela ndathi: ‘Hamba, ungagqithi apha; amaza akho adlokovayo makaphele apha.’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Ukhonje wakha wayiyalela intsasa yabakho? Wakha wasikhombisa indawo yaso na isifingo?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nditsho umsobomvu okhanyisela iziphelo zehlabathi, khon' ukuze izikhohlakali zingabi nakuzimela ebumnyameni.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kaloku ukusa kuzitsho ziphuhle iinduli neentili, zibe ngathi yingubo ebikade isongene; ewe, zitsho zicace oku kophawu olushicilelwe kumdongwe.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Abakhohlakeleyo bayoyiswa kukukhanya; kaloku ingalo yabo yokugonyamela yaphulwe.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Ngaba wakha wayibona imithombo yolwandle? Sowukhe wathi cakatha ezintunjini zenzonzobila?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Uwatyhilelwe na amasango okufa? Wakha wakubona kwamnyama-ndawo?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Khawutsho, lingakanani ihlabathi? Phendula kaloku ukuba uyazazi ezi zinto!",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Ungalixela apho likhoyo ikhaya lokukhanya? Khona, wona umthombo wobumnyama uphi?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ezi zinto ungazibuyisela na endaweni yazo? Khona, uyayazi na indlela esinga esikhundleni sazo?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Awunakungazazi; kaloku wawuseluzelwe, neminyaka yobomi bakho mininzi, ngabula wena!",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Wakha wababona oovimba bam bekhephu? Oovimba besichotho bona uyabazi?",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ezi zinto ndizigcinele mhla kwanyembeleka; ndizigcinele mhla kwathiwa ilizwe lifile.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Uyayazi na indlela eya apho kuvela khona ukukhanya? Uthini umoya wasempuma ukusasazeka phezu kwehlabathi?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ngubani ovulela izandyondyo zemvula umjelo; ingubani yena khona ovulela iindudumo indlela?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ngubani onisa imvula endle phaya? Inethiswa ngubani imvula enkqantosini,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ukuze ithobe unxano kumhlaba okhamisileyo, kutsho kuthi rhwelele utyani?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kakade, imvula le yinto kabani; ingubani yena uyise wombethe?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ke wona umkhenkce wakhawulwa ngubani; ingubani yena umzali weqabaka?",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kaloku amanzi ayaqina abe ngathi lilitye; inzongo-nzongo yamanzi itsho ikhenkcezele.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Uthi ngaba unokuzidibanisa izilimela; khona unako ukuwakhulula amakroza?",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ungazilawula iinkwenkwezi namathuba azo, nditsho oozibhere ngokunjalo namatakane azo?",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Uyayazi imithetho elawula ilanga nenyanga neenkwenkwezi? Unganako ukumisela impembelelo yazo emhlabeni?",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Unganako ukuliphakamisela emafini ilizwi lakho, khon' ukuze akugubungele ngezantyala-ntyala zemvula?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ngaba unganako ukuyithuma imibane? Ngaba ingavuma ithi: ‘Ndiyaya’?",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ngubani oyazisayo intsikizi ngemvula, ingubani oxelela umqhagi ngemini entsha?",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Sisiphi isilumko esinokubala amafu, ingubani onokuqubuda iingqayi zamanzi zasemazulwini?",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Nditsho imvula ejika uthuli lube ludaka, ke wona amagade atsho ancamathelane.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> “Unganako ukuzingelela imazi yengonyama? Ungawahluthisa khona amathole engonyama,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> xa ahleli esikhundleni sawo, okanye xa ancathame ngetyholo?",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Uthi ngubani owondla amahlungulu, xa amantshontsho awo akhala kuThixo, ebhadula ngenxa yendlala?"
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ngaba uyalazi ixesha lokuzala kwamagogo asemaweni? Wakha walibona na inxala xa lifikelwa yinimba yokuzala?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Lithatha iinyanga ezingakanani lithwele, lize lifike nini ke ixesha lokuzala kwalo?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Uyalazi ukuba lingqengqa nini na ukuze libeke itakane lalo, ibe ke ngokunjalo idlule intlungu yenimba?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Amatakane alo akhulela ezindle ade omelele, aze ke asuke emke angaze abe sabuya.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Iqwarha eli layithatha phi inkululeko? Ngubani owalikhulula intambo ukuba libhadule?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ndim owalinikela ukuba lihlale entlango, ikhaya lalo libe kuloo mathafa etyuwa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Isiphithi-phithi sasezixekweni yintlekisa kulo; ngokunjalo nemikhwazo yombhexeshi aliyiva.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Libhadula ezintabeni lifuna amadlelo, lize limemethe naluphi na uhlaza elilufumanayo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Uthi ungaze uyisebenzise inyathi? Unganako ukuyivalela ebuhlanti?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Uthi ungayirhintyela ulime ngayo; mhlawumbi uyerhe entilini phaya?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Uthi ingaze ikuncede ngamandla ayo; ungawunikela kuyo umsebenzi wakho?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngaba unganako ukuvuna ngayo? Uthi ungabhula ngayo esandeni phaya?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Hayi ukufaneleka kwamaphiko enciniba! Kambe ke iyagqweswa yingwamza ngokuphapha.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Amaqanda ayo iwabeka emhlabeni iwashiye ukuze ke afudunyezwe ngumhlaba lowo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ayinaloyiko lokuba osuka anyathelwe, okanye kuthi gqi inyamakazi iwakroboze.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ayinankathalo ngamantshontsho ayo, ngathi asingawayo; ayivakalelwa kukubhanga kwemigudu yayo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> UThixo uyivimbe ubulumko inciniba, akayinika nokuyinika ingqiqo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kambe ke yakuwathi naa amaphiko ayo ibaleka iyalihleka ihashe nokhwele kulo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Ngaba nguwe na owenze ihashe lomelela kangaka? Nguwe owalivathisa ngeso singci siyakayaka?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Nguwe olenze lanako ukuthi qakatha njengeenkumbi? Nguwe olenze larhwaqelisa ngesandi somfutho walo?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ligxanya ngamandla ngaloo manqina alo xa lijikela entilini phaya, selifunzele phakathi kwayiwayo!",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kaloku lona alinadyudyu nantaka; aliwazele nto umkhonto, alibuyi ngamva.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kaloku lo uphezu kwalo uxhob' uf' amacala; oomikhonto noozincula ziyabengezela.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngaloo manqina alo lisiphula umhlaba, selingasakwazi ukuzibamba, lilindele ukuvakala kwexilongo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Lakuva umtyangampo wexilongo lithi: ‘Ngxatsho ke!’ ze lithi lisekude lé, libe seliqonda ukuba izwe lifile! Kaloku liyabeva oomaqhuzu xa bayalelayo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Ngaba bubulumko bakho na obunika ukhetshe ubuchule bokubhabha? Nguwe omenza athi naa amaphiko abheke kwelasezantsi?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ngaba nguwe oyalela ixhalanga ukuba lintinge, lakhe nendlu yalo emalenga-lengeni phaya?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kaloku lona lihlala kwiinkelekethe zamawa; lizenzela inqaba kwiimfanta zamalenga-lenga.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Lithi cwaa apho lilonga-longe ixhoba, lize lilipopole noba selisekudeni.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Amathole alo amfimfitha igazi; nalapho zikhoyo izidumbu libutha khona ixhalanga.”"
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo uqhube wathi kuYobi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ngaba ufuna ukubambana noSomandla, usalatha iimpazamo zakhe? Wena omangalela uThixo, phendula.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ke yena uYobi uphendule *uNdikhoyo wathi:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Xa kungokunje ndiyaqonda ukuba andinto yanto. Ndingaba saphendula ndithini? Kungokunje ndidl' imu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ewe, ndithethe ndaphinda-phinda, kambe ke ngoku ndosuka ndiwuthunge.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ke *uNdikhoyo waphendula esesaqhwithini, wathetha noYobi wathi:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Khawuqule, ume njengendoda; mna ndiza kukubuza, wena ke uphendule.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Ngaba ufuna ukusisingela phantsi isigwebo sam? Ugweba mna ukuze wena ugwetyelwe?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngaba nawe womelele njengoThixo? Nelakho ilizwi lizongoma njengelakhe?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Xa kunjalo ke khawuvele uveth' isidima uzimasekile; khawuthi jize isihomo nesithozela.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Khawuphokoze loo msindo wakho, ubaphoxe abo bazigwagwisayo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ewe, badilize abo baqholosayo; ke zona izikhohlakali zinyhashele apho zikhoyo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Xa zizonke zibandakanye uzingcwabe; zigqume zihlale kwelo labafileyo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Xa kunjalo ke ndiya kuvuma, ndisithi unako ukuzisindisa ngawakho amandla.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Imvubu le uyayiqonda? Njengawe nayo ndayidala; phofu yona injengenkomo, itya ingca.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kambe ke, yeka – asimandla esinqeni sayo! Yinto emzimba unemisipha engwanyalala!",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Yinto emsila ungqangqasholo okomsedare; ke zona izihlunu zemilenze ziphindene.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Amathambo ayo omelele njengobhedu; ewe, afana nemivalo yentsimbi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kuzo zonk' izidalwa ithe kratya ngokukhwankqisa; nguMdali wayo yedwa onako ukuyoyisa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ukutya kwayo kufumaneka ezintabeni phaya, apho zidloba-dloba khona izilwanyana.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ungafika ingqengqe phantsi kwamatyholo akhula ngasemanzini, okanye izimele ezingcongolweni, emgxobhozweni phaya.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ewe, iphumla emthunzini wamatyholo entlanjeni phaya, ufike ijikelezwe yimingcunube.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Yona ayiwoyiki umlambo ophuphumayo; ithi zole nakwiJordan elatyuza amanzi de abethe emlonyeni wayo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kodwa kodwa ngubani ongayihlaselayo? Ngaba uqale wayityhaphaza? Ngubani ongayithiyela ayithi qhoo ngaloo mpumlo?"
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Uthi ungaze uyilobe ingwenya, okanye ubambe ulwimi lwayo ngentambo?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Uthi ungaze uyifake intambo impumlo yayo, mhlawumbi uyithi qhoo imihlathi ngegwegwe?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ucing' ukuba ingaze itarhuzise kuwe? Uthi ingakukubongoza ngamazwi athambileyo?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Uthi ingenza isivumelwano kunye nawe, ithembise ukuba likhoboka lakho ngonaphakade?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngaba ungayenza intaka ongadlalisa ngayo, uyikhulekele amantombazana akho?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Abarhwebi uthi bangarhweba ngayo? Ucing' ukuba bangahlulelana ngayo?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Isikhumba sayo ungasigqobhoza ngamagwegwe? Mkhonto waphi ongangxwelerha intloko yayo?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Khawuyichukumise nje – soz' uphinde! Engak' imfazwe soz' uyilibale!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngamampunge ukucinga ukuba ungayoyisa. Umntu uthi nje akuyibona asuke avikiveke aphelelwe.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kungekho bani nje unesibindi sokuyiphazamisa, ngubani ke ngoko onako ukumelana nam?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ukhona na onako ukubanga into kum ukuze ndimbuyisele? Kaloku yonke into phantsi kwezulu yeyam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Andinakuthi cwaka ngemilenze yayo; makhe ndikuphokozele ngokomelela kwayo nokufaneleka kokwakhiwa kwayo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngubani onokuyinyanzela ukuvula umlomo, ingubani onokuyifaka umkhala?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ewe, ngubani ongavula loo mihlathi yayo ijikelezwe ziingxavula ezoyikekayo zamazinyo?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Umqolo wayo unoludwe lwamakhaka aphotheneyo ngathi atywiniwe.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ewe, asondelelene ayimbumba; phakathi kwawo akungeni nomoya.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hayi, anxibelelene angunonca, abambene nkwa, akanakwahlukaniswa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Yintw' ethi yakuthimla kumenyeze, emehlo ngathi lilanga liphuma.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Yintw' emlomo ulatyuza amadangatye, kutsho kutak' iintlantsi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Yintw' emarhanana alephuz' umsi, oku kwembiza ebaselwe ngeengcongolo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngomphefumlo wayo ungáwuphemb' umlilo; kaloku kuthaphuz' amadangatye kuloo mlomo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Yintw' etsho ngengwanyalala yesixhanti; bakuyibona abantu suka barhwaqele.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Izihlunu zayo zifumbene; ziyingwanyalala engenakuhluthuzwa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Yintw' entliziyo iqine oku kwenyengane! Yomelele oku kwelitye lokusila.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ithi ingaphakama kunkwantye neengangalala; yakushukuma zisuka zithi phithi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Yona yomelele, ayinakungxwelerhwa naziintshuntshe, oomikhonto, noozincula.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kuyo intsimbi ifana nomququ; ke lona ubhedu nqwa nevithi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Okukokwalo utolo ayilwazele nto; kuyo ilitye *lenkwitshi linkumnka ngathi sisabhunge.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ke lona ibhunguza lifana nodiza; iincula ziyinto yentsini kuyo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Isisu sayo nqwa namaceba embiza; umhlaba siwukrazula oku kwesileyi sokubhula.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Amanzi enzonzobila iwatsho abile okwembiza, ulwandle iluzama-zamise okweqhaga leziqholo.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Emva kwayo ngumzila omenyezelayo emanzini. Inzonzobila isuka ifane neenwele zengwevu.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ehlabathini akukho nto inokulinganiswa nayo, nditsho isilo esingenabo ubugwala.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kaloku noozindlula-mthi izikrobile; ewe, ingukumkani kwizilo zonke ezinyalasayo.”"
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku uYobi uphendule *uNdikhoyo wenjenje:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ewe, ngoku ndiyaqonda ukuba wena unako ukufeza konke; konke okucebayo wena unako ukukwenza.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bendingubani ukufuna ukulenza mfiliba icebo lakho, ndingenalwazi nje? Ngenene ndigabadele, ndithethiswa kukungaqondi; ndithethe ngemimangaliso nezinto ezinkulu kunam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Uthe kum: ‘Phulaphula, mna ndiza kukubuza, wena ke uphendule.’",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngoko bendikwazi nje ngokuva ngeendlebe, kambe ke ngoku ndikubonile ngala wam amehlo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngenxa yale nto ke ngoku ndiyazisola; ewe, ndiyaguquka; ndiseluthulini naseluthuthwini.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Emva kwale ntetho *kaNdikhoyo noYobi uNdikhoyo ubhekise kuElifazi waseTema, wathi: “Umsindo wam uyavutha kuwe nakubahlobo bakho ababini, kuba anithethanga nto iyiyo ngam njengesicaka sam uYobi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ngoko ke thathani iinkunzi zeenkomo ezisixhenxe, neenkunzi zeegusha ezikwasixhenxe, niye nazo kwisicaka sam uYobi, nizenzele idini elitshiswayo. Ke yena uYobi isicaka sam uya kunithandazela; ibe ke mna ndiya kuwamkela loo mthandazo wakhe, ndinganiphathi ngokobudenge benu. Kaloku nina anithethanga nto iyiyo ngam njengoko enzileyo yena uYobi isicaka sam.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngenene ke uElifazi waseTeman noBhildadi waseShuwa noZofare waseNama benza ngokomlomo *kaNdikhoyo, waza ke yena wawamkela umthandazo kaYobi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Akuba ke uYobi ebathandazele abahlobo bakhe kuNdikhoyo, uNdikhoyo waphinda wambuyisela uYobi kundalashe. Ewe, ubutyebi bakhe wada wabuphinda-phinda.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Abantakwabo noodade bakhe, ngokunjalo nâbo babemazi ngaphambili, beza, batya kunye naye emzini wakhe. Bavelana naye, bamkhuza bemthuthuzela ngenxa yesithwakumbe awayebethwe ngaso nguNdikhoyo. Bonke ngabanye ngabanye bamnika imali nomsesane wegolide.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ke kaloku uNdikhoyo walithamsanqela ikamva likaYobi nangaphezu kokuba wayenzile kubomi bakhe bangaphambili. UYobi waba neshumi elinesine lamawaka eegusha, isithandathu samawaka eenkamela, amawaka amabini eenkabi zeenkomo newaka leedonki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Waphiwa isixhenxe soonyana neentombi zantathu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Eyokuqala yayinguJimayima, kweza uKeziya, eyesithathu ke yanguKeren-hapuka.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kulo lonke ihlabathi akukho ntombi yayifika kwezo ntombi zikaYobi ngobunzwakazi. Nazo ke uyise wazinika ilifa kwanjengabantakwazo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Emva koku ke uYobi wahlala iminyaka elikhulu elinamashumi amane. Ewe, wada wabona abazukulwana nabantwana babo kwada kwaya kuthi xhaxhe ngesesine isizukulwana.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ke kaloku uYobi wafa seleyingwevu, iminyaka selihambile."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;